ondary jumps during the three-tier, fifteen-year-old entered the University of California, joined Google before Microsoft and other companies.) <br /><br /> The last three years, as Google (Google) software engineer, my weekly review of your resume will help the personnel department, decided to not give them interviews. Google make a lot of development in recent years many excellent engineers have come to apply. So far, I have seen thousands of resumes, resume the impression that some much better than others. Especially relatives and friends often ask me recently how to modify their resume, so I have some proposals to avoid common mistakes in this exchange with you about. <br /><br /> 1. When you are done talking about the technology, programming language used should be mentioned, your individual contributions and product details. <br /><br /> Sometimes I see someone put on a resume of past experience in passing, for example: <br /><br /> Ã¢Â€Â¢ In three of the group, write e-mail software, some features. <br /><br /> It is not enough to see resumes of people want to know the difficulty of the work you do and how much contact the company, so you better write the specific. For example: <br /><a name=\"entrymore\"></a><br /> Ã¢Â€Â¢ Use C + + language to write the network e-mail automatically backups. In three of the group, responsible for design and write storage server. Starting from the design, one year after the feature this functionality pushed to the thousand of users. <br /><br /> 2. More facts, fewer adjectives. <br /><br /> View Resume of people read your resume, you need to make judgments, so in your resume need facts and numbers. If you write &quot;rapidly improve the efficiency of operation of the software&quot; to see your resume is very difficult to judge success more difficult. But if you write &quot;in 3 weeks, the software operating efficiency is improved by 40%&quot; much better. <br /><br /> Some humble words full of friends who do not want to, so you can also use this approach. If you say that they &quot;outstanding&quot; or &quot;in the project often was asked to put out the fire,&quot; inevitably sounds a little proud. But you can also use can not be denied to illustrate your point of view, such as &quot;&quot; New York Daily News &quot;Review this product as \'outstanding\'&quot;, or &quot;joined the three had been behind schedule in the project team, but through hard work and group member of them all together was completed on time. &quot; <br /><br /> 3. You get the award, honor or recognition of business, popular with users of the product and the difficulty you have done the amateur projects included in the resume. <br /><br /> I have a friend in a well-known Silicon Valley hardware company for six years, she designed the IP phone (VoIP) for the company hundreds of millions earned income reported by the company several times and commercial evaluation of the award. I once driving on the highway in San Francisco when I saw a roadside billboard with her products; Another time I went to Shanghai on vacation, even the side roads are also found in Shanghai! <br /><br /> Soon, the friend decided to change, please I look at her resume. I was surprised to find that she even wrote an understatement - &quot;1998 - 2004: Internet telephony products, hardware engineers, team leader,&quot; and her duties. <br /><br /> &quot;Product to win the award? It is the company money?&quot; I asked to. <br /><br /> &quot;Those are the write?&quot; She said. <br /><br /> Of course the writing. <br /><br /> Some people ask, Can you spare time to write the project? I think as long as the performance of your project on behalf of your ability that would have to include. <br /><br /> 4. Prioritize, delete insignificant compared to the results, so as not to dilute the more prominent achievements. <br /><br /> A friend asked, to write a resume is not written better? For example: <br /><br /> A summer intern in the company to do - <br /> * To improve the value of video games classification algorithm, reducing memory requirements by 10%. <br /> * Use Java to write a 3,000-line user interface program. <br /> * Two hours a week to do manual testing. <br /><br /> Your position in the application software engineer, I feel more related to the former two, the third point of fact, do not have to write. Sometimes I see some resume will be mentioned, &quot;time to complete the task, the products meet the specifications of the original plan.&quot; But reading your resume will usually take it for granted, but instead you put these statements out of the effect of weakening your resume. <br /><br /> Write a resume is not easy, but will also have a sense of accomplishment written (and good job!). Google (Google) in China, widely called all aspects of personnel, you may wish to vote can give us a resume! We are not only in terms of recruiting engineers, information retrieval, as well as computer graphics, user interfaces, hardware, Windows, quality assurance staff and system administrators and so on. For more information, please visit here. <br /><br /> Thank you for reading! We are interested, next time I can recommend &quot;How to prepare software engineer interview.&quot; </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>',' (Author: Wang Xin, Google engineers. Beijing born parents moved to the U.S. to follow the age of five. Secondary jumps during the three-tier, fifteen-year-old entered the University of California, joined Google before Microsoft and other companies.)  The last three years, as Google (Google)...'),(73,'Linux','linux','en','/a/os/linux/2010/0707/283.html','http://www.ixdba.net','php linux systems and solutions related to the error summary','php_linux_systems_and_solutions_related_to_the_error_summary','2010-07-07','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> Problem symptoms and error message: </p><p class=\"code\"> Exception message: fsockopen (): php_network_getaddresses: getaddr