liefs or convictions, has his mission. However, most of who we really are able to personally feel this mission? This is not necessarily. But one thing, we believe the company, we believe that Ma, believe in him. Followed him how to say, on how to go. Instant wrong, take us to adjust the direction, adjusting the path we ultimately take a decade. Longer follow the words of the future, we must follow this principle has been moving forward. <br /> This process is the price we paid what we are depressed, White did last year. The past is the focus of the project, focusing on products, is no longer the focus, and changed direction, and this is the growing costs. But we can not feel the leadership is fanciful gang, a gang of pig brain. <br /> Perhaps we feel that he is very smart, but I deeply feel that we do not wisdom. Intelligence and wisdom are really two things. </p><p> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\">Summary</span> <br /> Our technical people to do more practical sense of commitment, to break through the self to influence others. Including other people, including Ma, including Xu Zhu, he wants to influence, are also such a process. Each area is such a process. From this perspective, are interlinked. He ought to complete his mission, he also requires us to break through ourselves. So, all of this all, you can find a common thing. <br /> I hope we can come to a serious, serious thinking about this problem. Think about how to do each of us, do not wait, not policies, not so competent. Everyone from me, from now on. Do you think you want, then what do you think you want to communicate more with others. I want to see what is not a deviation, is not it may not be reasonable? More collisions with others, communicate more with different people, you will find, in fact, everyone, all kinds of ideas, one very interesting, the second is in the process, you can go to sum up, to summarize, to refining, can be sublimated . <br /> So, I give herself reasons. To talk about life, talk about ideals, in fact, is the essence behind this: I want to see how everyone is thinking, why each of us have standards for everyone, but also deeply course, but others not so recognized you. How do we break through this predicament? That is why I trust to talk about this topic. <br /> Because I think that this matter is not resolved, we recruit more people, have been grinding out our low efficiency, the more the fat, this is the problem we must address so that we can move forward to support the company health go. I\'m finished, thank you. </p></div></div> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>',' Biti\'s a sentiment article: the original link Very pleased to have opportunity to speak here. Lu Su is not the same as me and the two types of people, I belong to the sense of genre, so the PPT only a page. Wei Yan has just said in the introduction, when Lu Su, Lu Su and functioning as a...'),(127,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0928/790.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Novell as a Linux operating...','Novell_as_a_Linux_operating','2010-09-28','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Novell as a <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/\">Linux</a></u> operating system vendor, has been in the <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/\">Linux</a></u> area is not red nor the survival of the fire. However, it is put in consideration the hands of the SUSE Linux operating system, Linux is likely to be of the traditional pattern of a powerful weapon. <br /> Linux industry, the traditional pattern, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu Linux form the top three. Despite the apparently Ubuntu does not encroach on enterprise Linux market, but in some workstation hardware, Ubuntu is quite a market. <br /> According to &quot;The Wall Street Journal&quot; reported that, VMware could get their Linux Novell acquired assets. Novell VMware is in talks to buy one of the many manufacturers. Novell is currently being considered for divestment, including VMware is working with at least two vendors, including high-level talks. <br /> Thus, if once acquired VMware hand, will help VMware in the context of broader market into the clouds. VMware is the virtualization of the most powerful companies, once for SUSE Linux and VMware virtualization technology in conjunction with, will inevitably create a strong competitor to Red Hat, the impact of the latter is self-evident. As a result, Red Hat Linux\'s dominant position, most likely not be maintained. <br /> Another way of saying that the acquisition of SUSE Linux is probably IBM. IBM and Red Hat have many years of cooperation, if IBM is determined to acquire SuSE, whether it will continue to maintain this relationship depends on how IBM SuSE have a bit of hope. May in any case, once the IBM acquisition of SuSE, in the next few years will pose a threat to Red Hat, although a direct financial impact will not be more than 60 million per year. <br /> More worse, IBM has used the line software and hardware product lines. IBM back in 2000 to drop it into the billions of dollars to support Linux, and now all of its product line can be no barrier into Linux. Once the full support of some kind of IBM Linux, its influence is limitless. <br /> There is also a view that he may come forward to buy Red Hat, SUSE Linux. However, because Red Hat and SUSE high degree of overlap of business and the acquisition would mean in the next 5 to 7 years, have to bear the financial support of SuSE. Therefore, the Red Hat acquisition is unlikely. But only this possibility is the Red Hat Linux to consolidate its industry in the boss position. The combination of SUSE and Red Hat, but also may give the next part of the brand of Linux to the market space. <br /> Indeed, the rise of Linux has by no means the brand is not possible. September 21, Oracle\'s global technology and application of the General Assembly, Oracle announced that Oracle software and hardware to optimize the introduction of a fast, modern and reliable enterprise-class Oracle Unbreakable Linux kernel core. Within the Oracle software and hardware industrial chain has improved steadily after, Oracle Unbreakable Linux is playing an increasingly larger stage. And industry experts generally believe that Oracle\'s acquisition of VMware may also far less great, and Oracle\'s acquisition will not cause too much of the current market share. <br /> Thus, with the approaching date of acquisition SUSE Linux, Red Hat\'s leadership position may not be preserved, Oracle Unbreakable Linux is constantly looking for the opportunity to host. The most elusive is the SUSE Linux, it decided to change the industry, but also to sway their own destiny to become uncertain. Regardless of where to change, Linux industry may be at the eve of regime change.</span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','Novell as a Linux operating system vendor, has been in the Linux area is not red nor the survival of the fire. However, it is put in consideration the hands of the SUSE Linux operating system, Linux is likely to be of the traditional pattern of a powerful weapon.  Linux industry, the traditional...'),(128,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0924/788.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Linus Trovalds rarely appeared...','Linus_Trovalds_rarely_appeared','2010-09-24','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linus Trovalds rarely appeared at the meeting, standing in front of the crowd is very little speech for him. However, he made an exception to participate in the August, held in Brazil <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/\">Linux</a></u> Con General Assembly, at which he and Andrew Morton has joined the <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/\">Linux</a></u> Foundation Jim Zemlin President of Q &amp; A session chaired. The conversation related to the kernel development process and development history, and many other topics.</span></span> </p><div style=\"text-align: center\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"314\" onclick=\"window.open(&apos;/uploads/allimg/100924/1_100924132211_1.png&apos;)\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.net/uploads/allimg/100924/1_100924132211_1.png\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" width=\"484\" /></span></span> </div><p> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Question 1: Is it conceivable that such a large Linux development?</span></span></strong> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Jim opening to ask: do not know if Andrew had not thought about Linus and Linux developed to become so big? Linus\'s answer is no; He said he wrote the original Linux only as a short-term projects, and ready to use better the to be replaced. Because the GNU project and was also very good BSD camp, he thought there must be other people to make more powerful and more professional to the core. At the same time, when he was just a little Linux as their love only. Funny when Andrew added: &quot;However, the final proof, no one was doing better than Linux. I, as a kernel rookie (humble way, in fact, Andrew in this area at least 10 years), although not very long vision, but I personally think that Linux is indeed very alarming development. &quot;</span></span> </p><p> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Question 2: How do you cope with the rapid development of the kernel?</span></span></strong> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Jim then asked, How do you cope with the rapid development of the kernel? Andrew said, as the core of continuous improvement, the number of developers who continue to expand. The development of core responsibilities assigned to each person then, and now I just take the Linux Linus total project only a small part of the work. Quality assurance in the code the dealer has played a big role. Based on this, Andrew said that just now the kernel community to provide technical, but the dealer can get the kernel from the community, and then into actual products.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linus on the Linux kernel that in general people are not interested in things. For example, he said he always felt that <span class=\"nounderline\">the server</span> market is a boring place, but was successfully applied to shift the Linux <span class=\"nounderline\">servers.</span> This is also one of the main advantages of Linux, Linus pointed out that no company would be interested in all uses of Linux, but their effect is often used for Linux, that he was amazed. He expressed some areas of Linux applications and even he did not expect. This also means that no one needs to use the Linux kernel users of the product while maintaining full responsibility for the negative. In particular, Linus, the real need is to care for myself, to ensure that all of the code fragment into together. After all, the power of a single kernel is limited, can not satisfy all application requirements, it can do is to constantly improve the core, allowed to meet the wider environment.</span></span> </p><p> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Question 3: Is it wise to continue to use the single-core? Single core can be applied to multi-task environment? Handle fragmentation, when this particular task is not to temporarily give up multi-core features?</span></span></strong> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">From this interview, Jim asked to split the kernel, as well as Linux continues to use the wisdom of a single core, while the single core is suitable for multi-tasking environment; future to support the development needs of different areas will separate out the different versions of the core issues .</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linus that the single-core to work well, he is also very annoying to see Linux division. Present problems in many areas there is a commonality in fact, for example, when the field of Linux used in <span class=\"nounderline\">mobile phones,</span> then the system for <span class=\"nounderline\">power</span> management requires more points, but proved to <span class=\"nounderline\">servers, power</span> management is also very important. In general, users in different application areas of concern in fact the same thing, only concerned the timing is different. Only high-end <span class=\"nounderline\">server</span> applications, such as who will be concerned in the symmetric multiprocessing, and now is basically to buy a desktop computer does not support SMP, right, and now SMP is also used in <span class=\"nounderline\">mobile phones</span> in the. This is the single-core approach has the advantage: If the <span class=\"nounderline\">phone</span> user needs SMP support, Linux always waiting for you.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Andrew said that Linux is widely used mainly due to the unique technical properties of the kernel. Linux kernel is now very easy to work together. The current Linux kernel has been the efforts of everyone from the original &quot;small&quot; devices become more and more. Unfortunately, there are still many small embedded systems in the community is still not very good technical support, but the Linux community as a whole is very concerned about this part of the body, embedded in the future we will also give good technical support groups .</span></span> </p><p> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Question 4: Where is the kernel development workers, mainly from Brazil to the kernel developers to participate in the development come from?</span></span></strong> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linus responded that, Linux kernel developers are mainly from North America, Europe and Australia. Because of cultural and language differences, increasing the difficulty of the entire community management. Linus said to run a global project, first of all need to solve the problem of language commonality, Linus is also fun to say: &quot;Unfortunately, instead of using the Finnish community (Linus is Finnish).&quot; Linus said that the world has a lot of good developers, But at the same time difficult to find good developers who are good at English. In order to solve regional and language and cultural differences, Linus said that they usually work is to establish a local community, and then connect these communities as a bridge to other communities and headquarters.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Andrew pointed out that obviously many people in Japan in recent years to participate in kernel development to; he recorded a lot of efforts on the Linux Foundation, the community members. He also found that people use Email for communication between non-native is helpful; because both sides have enough time to understand each other\'s meaning. As to where to start communication, Andrew opinion is to choose an interesting and challenging work begins.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linus that open source software is programmed to understand the world situation in a good way. Unlike the class open source projects, an active project needs and communicate together to solve the problem. Some companies in need of technical personnel, often in the open source community to find those activists. Therefore, to participate in open source projects, but also to the world a good way to promote their own. Finally, Linus said that it is difficult to find good programmers, they generally get good pay, they often work for open source software. Andrew also agreed to have the firm belief that programmers are widely available light. The time at Google, Andrew often issued to him by a number of internal staff qualifications, to hire whom he chooses. He made the first move was to open the git log to see who has done what in the community activities.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linus said that although the kernel may not be a good starting point to learn the best programmers. However, there are many kernel developers, people often think that the kernel is very mysterious, and even have a psychological fear of approaching. The initial development of small projects for those who are a good starting environment.</span></span> </p><p> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Question 5: Will never work for Linux?</span></span></strong> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linus replied, &quot;Never is a very long time,&quot; he initially only to the kernel as a two-month project, but he said they would continue to do the kernel, because now he felt fun. Because there will always be new problems to be solved and new hardware</span></span>Need to compatible. This interesting project he has done for 19 years, and still last a long time to do the kernel. </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Interview with Jim doing the final summary of the General Assembly, mainly cited Linus and Andrew for the Linux kernel contributions. When Jim was impressed that Linus and Andrew are in the technical field of the two most influential people. They and Bill Gates,, Steve Jobs, Larry Ellison and the same level. They are the world\'s most rich. Linus and Andrew have looked in the Jim said: &quot;You crazy?&quot; What is your motivation?. &quot;And then laughter.</span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','Linus Trovalds rarely appeared at the meeting, standing in front of the crowd is very little speech for him. However, he made an exception to participate in the August, held in Brazil Linux Con General Assembly, at which he and Andrew Morton has joined the Linux Foundation Jim Zemlin President of Q...'),(129,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0917/719.html','http://www.ixdba.net','For some time, inside the...','For_some_time_inside_the','2010-09-17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">For some time, inside the circle of developers, many of Apple, and iPhone OS platforms (including the iPhone, iPod touch, iPad) voice of criticism, the main criticism of this platform is not open. Some critics are very sincere and hit crucial point, and some entirely groundless, incorrectly relay an erroneous.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">First, the opening is not a simple concept.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Before the advent of smart phones, mobile phone operating system manufacturer is often proprietary, the software is often built above, and only manufacturer to develop the above procedures, but most machines do not support installing new software. This is the real closed.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">With smart phones, though a large number of platforms and languages we can use, but did not actually form a robust application development market.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">J2ME applications to the mobile phone market had illusions of prosperity. But in fact, on the one hand, in order to ensure compatibility, J2ME give up a lot of features, performance and application scenarios are greatly limited, difficult to develop and sell the user a powerful and easy to use program.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">In another aspect, it is no perfect interface and operational standards, support of various kinds of mobile phones after the fact, compatibility and completely can not be guaranteed, very few programs can support a variety of mobile phones is really perfect particular game type applications, really be compatible with a variety of mobile phone rare.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Nokia S40 and S60 adhere to the two fronts, on the standardization and product diversity to achieve a relatively good balance. Once considered the savior of mobile applications market, however, the past 10 years, Nokia\'s mobile phones although the appearance of each passing day, but the software and operating system improvements inadequate. And the difficulty of system development has been too high Symbian, Nokia Symbian platform and no momentum in the best of times AppStore launch such a business model similar to it. Therefore, since the advent of iPhone, a lot of developers interested in mobile developers, Nokia and the Symbian platform started to give up.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Now, no matter the platform for mobile application from the quantity, quality, and the developer\'s revenue, we can say that Apple iPhone is the mobile application market really began to boom.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Of course no doubt that Apple is indeed very close in some ways. But I do not think it is bad children.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Picture of the future of the software industry should not only open source software, only commercial software, or software only under the AppStore. Three different modes, each other to form a very good supplement.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">In the iPhone / iPod touch, and specific areas such iPad, AppStore model is incredibly powerful. Apple earnings to see you will know how much this opens up a third-party software market. The concept of smart phones appeared almost 10 years, has never been a platform, bringing together so many third-party developers, so many excellent free and paid applications. Previously, third-party developers are making money of course, but the scale and form together in such a platform is unprecedented.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Assuming iPhone OS platform, all the same, just remove the AppStore, we will find that many are now third-party developers to get rich, they just only in the dreams of fortune. Therefore, a certain degree of closure is not necessarily a root of all evil.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">It is because when the issue in the application of the strict need Apple Developer Certificate signed by the greatest extent in the prevention of piracy, making sales of a variety of payment applications have been guaranteed. It is also because of criticism by many people can even say that is too strict quality audits to ensure only the procedures within the AppStore has a certain quality level, which would allow consumers to enjoy in the AppStore in to look and buy more procedures.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">What\'s more, Apple\'s next picture, the only piece of gorgeous, not all. Open source / commercial / AppStore three modes, I think that their own strength in the future, will have their place.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">I have repeatedly stressed that, like open people, the mentality is more to open. Some people do not want to allow the open source world, do not want to open, this is an open mind. You love CopyLeft, you could have your code open sourced. But CopyLeft not include forcing others to the spirit of open source (subject to licensing restrictions would result in a different matter.)</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">I also agree with the spirit of open source, open source projects themselves, are being maintained, but do these open source projects, and I made such a relatively closed iPhone platform for the above items, did not create any conflict.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">I would like to see in the next open source / commercial / AppStore three models, fancy, are booming. In fact, the rise of open source, and not kill the business, but expanded our vision of the entire software industry and territory. App Store also has a similar role, I look forward to it gives me more to come.</span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','For some time, inside the circle of developers, many of Apple, and iPhone OS platforms (including the iPhone, iPod touch, iPad) voice of criticism, the main criticism of this platform is not open. Some critics are very sincere and hit crucial point, and some entirely groundless, incorrectly relay an...'),(130,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0917/718.html','http://www.ixdba.net','According to The Wall Street...','According_to_The_Wall_Street','2010-09-17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">According to The Wall Street Journal reported that several sources said, Novell is working with VMware, including at least two potential buyers, including negotiations to sell its business. <br /> The source said, VMware wants to acquire Novell\'s SUSE <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/\"><span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"tag.php?name