,'/a/IT/2010/0430/90.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Red Hat Linux Enterprise Edition RHEL6 beta version of Fat','Red_Hat_Linux_Enterprise_Edition_RHEL6_beta_version_of_Fat','2010-04-30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p class=\"newtext\"> Red Hat Enterprise <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/\">Linux</a></u> has released the first version of the past 8 years. Since the release date, the product established as a leading enterprise-class open source operating <a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/\"><u>system,</u></a> one of the position. Installation of <a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/\"><u>the system</u></a> used in portable computer to the mainframe from a variety of machines to help establish the quality certification infrastructure, long-term stability, performance, and security models. From the main street to Wall Street, Red Hat Enterprise <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/\">Linux</a></u> into almost all walks of life. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Red Hat Enterprise Linux into the Beta testing, the currently supported versions: Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5, Red Hat is still the cornerstone of the portfolio of software products. Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5 in March 2007 was first released, self-released, through a number of regularly updated. Last month, we have just released the Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5 the 5th updated with new features and hardware support. In 2014, Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5 platform, Red Hat will continue to be, and its ISV and OEM partners for their support. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Looking to the future, Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 blurred virtual, physical, and the boundaries between cloud computing to adapt to contemporary changes occurring in IT environments. Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 from the kernel to the application infrastructure to the development tool chain is used to upgrade the core technology to meet the future generations of hardware and software technology needs. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> New version of the theme, including the ubiquitous virtualization, better stability and high availability, higher energy efficiency and to provide more than the latest software technology. Beta version released today on the occasion, we will introduce several new and noteworthy improvements: </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Comprehensive power management capabilities </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ time kernel to improve the system there will be no more frequently active task processor becomes idle state. This will lead to a lower temperature than previous versions and higher CPU power saving. Powertop other new monitoring tools that can help identify energy problems can be solved, thus further reducing energy consumption. Like a &quot;tuned&quot; so that the new regulation tool (an adaptive system regulating daemon) service the system can adjust the energy usage pattern analysis. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Performance Improvement </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ Red Hat engineers we plan to appear in Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 performance improvements in a variety of upstream development kernel play a key role in the process of completely rewriting the scheduler so that it can make the process a higher priority at the lowest limit lower priority treatment under the conditions of interference, a more equitable distribution among the processor computation time. In addition, for a variety of multi-processor lock synchronization improvements. For example, to eliminate unnecessary lock events, many of rotation instead of using the sleep lock (spin) lock and a more efficient locking primitives. Impact of these fundamental changes to many core subsystems. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Improved scalability </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ The new hardware has led to major developments in commodity computing platforms. For example, now a 5U rack cabinet can hold 64 CPU and 2TB of memory. These systems and their subsequent products will be Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5 to achieve the scalability limits. Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 is one of the main features: it can provide scalability to adapt to future systems. The scalability of capacity from a large number of CPU and memory configuration for the optimization of the support to handle a larger number of systems the ability to interconnect bus and peripherals. With bare metal virtualization becomes ubiquitous, like the time of deployment, the ability of the environment suitable for bare metal and virtual environments. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> New security features </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ called security services daemon (SSSD) of the new service provides a centralized identity management. It also has a cache for offline use certificate capabilities. New SELinux sandbox feature allows untrusted content can not affect the system in an isolated environment for the rest of the run. This includes the isolation of any Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 running on a virtual client capabilities. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Resource Management </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ called in a control group (ie cgroups) with the help of a new framework, the new system provides the hardware resources of fine-grained control, distribution and management. cgroups running in process group level, can be used for application management from the CPU, memory, network and disk I / O resources. The framework is also used to manage virtual clients. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Virtualization </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 extends the earlier versions of Red Hat Enterprise Linux integrated virtualization based on KVM technology. The new system has more than one performance, scheduler and hardware improvements, no matter what the deployment model to provide better flexibility and control. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Storage </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ FCoE and iSCSI protocols through the network block storage support, so use LVM / DM to change the implementation of online and multi-path mirrored volume size possible. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> File System </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ new system includes the ext4 file system. Extended family of next-generation file system, which includes support for larger file sizes, more efficient disk space allocation, better and more robust file system check log. In addition to ext4, we also intend to provide XFS? File system. XFS? For large files and directories, including debris removal and the like when used in the file system the ability to change the file system size. Level has risen to NFS version 4, which includes IPv6 support. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Reliability, availability and serviceability (RAS) </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ new version of the use of new hardware hot-add capability to provide equipment and hardware as well as through AER\'s PCIe device features such as enhanced error checking. It will also include advanced data integrity features (DIF / DIX). Such characteristics of the hardware from the application of inspection and survey data. ABRT (automatic bug report tool) provides the introduction of the system to identify and report anomalies such as the core DD fault (kernel oops) and user space applications crash DD more consistent manner. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Compilers and tools </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Ã¢Â—Â‹ GCC compiler has been upgraded to version 4.4. This version of the draft in accordance with C + + 0x standard compilation. It is also consistent with OpenMP 3.0, includes a number of debugging. SystemTap improvements include better user support for space exploration, more secure server and compile the script so that non-root user can access the SystemTap the new non-privileged mode. In addition, there are many other new compiler has been upgraded to the latest version of the library and more languages and operating environment, including a complete LAMP stack and OpenJDK. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Desktop </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Introduced a new version of the display type of testing and support for multiple monitors. We also added support for NVIDIA graphics device driver for the upgrade of the new. Of course, if GNOME and KDE desktop does not update the new version will be incomplete. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 in a variety of technology hardware platform as the key to the expansion of support provided, we believe that these technologies will become a new platform to attract new customers an attractive choice. As always, the new version is part of the value of our enterprise certification. </p><p class=\"newtext\"> Currently, thousands of applications in Red Hat Enterprise Linux by running the certification, whether it runs on &quot;bare metal&quot; deployment, virtualization deployment, or cloud deployment. This makes Red Hat Enterprise Linux to become the first choice for customers and partners operating system. </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>',' Red Hat Enterprise Linux has released the first version of the past 8 years. Since the release date, the product established as a leading enterprise-class open source operating system, one of the position. Installation of the system used in portable computer to the mainframe from a variety of...'),(132,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0422/54.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 announced that will no longer','Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux_6_announced_that_will_no_longer','2010-04-22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p></p><div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"350\" onclick=\"window.open(&apos;/uploads/allimg/100422/1_100422144350_1.jpg&apos;)\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.net/uploads/allimg/100422/1_100422144350_1.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" width=\"318\" /><br /></div><p> <strong>Red Hat said in a statement Sunday that its next major release of Linux operating system, version of &quot;Enterprise Linux 6&quot; will give up on Intel Itanium processors.</strong> </p><p> According to market research firm IDC research manager for European systems division, said Chris Ingle, to abandon support for Red Hat Itanium processors have economic interests. Itanium processor-based server sales may not be too much, not enough to prove that it invest in Red Hat support for enterprise Linux Itanium operating system is reasonable. On the contrary, it will focus on support for x86 servers. </p><p> Currently, Red Hat\'s &quot;Enterprise Linux 5&quot; support the IBM Power processor-based servers, System z servers and S/390 processor architecture. <br /><br /> Ingle, IDC said, for users, Red Hat to abandon support for Itanium is not much difference, because most vendors have received from the OEM manufacturers technical support. <br /><br /> Red Hat in March 2014 before the still running on the Itanium server &quot;Enterprise Linux 5&quot; for technical support. Red Hat will run on Itanium server &quot;Enterprise Linux 5&quot; to add new features and product life cycle in accordance with its standard policy of support for new hardware. </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','Red Hat said in a statement Sunday that its next major release of Linux operating system, version of \"Enterprise Linux 6\" will give up on Intel Itanium processors. According to market research firm IDC research manager for European systems division, said Chris Ingle, to abandon support for Red Hat...'),(133,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0422/53.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL) 6 beta','Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux_RHEL_6_beta','2010-04-22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"180\" onclick=\"window.open(&apos;/uploads/allimg/100422/1_100422143041_1.png&apos;)\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.net/uploads/allimg/100422/1_100422143041_1_lit.png\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" width=\"555\" /><br /><br /> <span>Red Hat has just released Enterprise Linux RHEL 6.0 in the Beta version, the version of the most noteworthy improvements include:</span> </div><ul><li> <span>Comprehensive power management features</span> </li><li> <span>Performance</span> </li><li> <span>Enhanced Scalability</span> </li><li> <span>The new security features</span> </li><li> <span>Virtualization</span> </li><li> <span>Storage improvements, support the FCoE and iSCSI support network block device</span> </li><li> <span>EXT4 file system support</span> </li><li> <span>Reliability, availability, and applicability</span> </li><li> <span>Enhanced Compilation Tools - GCC 4.4</span> </li><li> <span>Improved desktop, support for multiple virtual desktops</span> </li></ul><p> The following address to download the Beta version: </p><p> <a href=\"http://www.redhat.com/rhel/beta/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.redhat.com/rhel/beta/</a> </p><p> <a href=\"http://ftp.redhat.com/redhat/rhel/beta/6/i386/iso/RHEL6.0-20100414.0-AP-i386-DVD1.iso\">RHEL6.0-AP-i386-DVD1.iso</a> (3,650 MB, <a href=\"http://ftp.redhat.com/redhat/rhel/beta/6/i386/iso/SHA256SUM\">SHA256</a> ) <br /> <a href=\"http://ftp.redhat.com/redhat/rhel/beta/6/x86_64/iso/RHEL6.0-AP-x86_64-DVD1.iso\">RHEL6.0-20,100,414.0-AP-x86_64-DVD1.iso</a> (4,105 MB, <a href=\"http://ftp.redhat.com/redhat/rhel/beta/6/x86_64/iso/SHA256SUM\">SHA256</a> ). </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','Red Hat has just released Enterprise Linux RHEL 6.0 in the Beta version, the version of the most noteworthy improvements include:Comprehensive power management featuresPerformanceEnhanced ScalabilityThe new security featuresVirtualizationStorage improvements, support the FCoE and iSCSI support...'),(134,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0422/55.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Tomcat 5.5.29 release','Tomcat_5529_release','2010-04-22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p></p><div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"129\" onclick=\"window.open(&apos;/uploads/allimg/100422/1_100422144825_1.jpg&apos;)\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.net/uploads/allimg/100422/1_100422144825_1.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" width=\"268\" /></div><p> <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/web/tomcat/\">Tomcat</a></u> 5.5 is an older version, just released 5.5.29 version mainly fixes some serious bug, but also to upgrade a number of Java class libraries, such as commons-pool and so on. </p><p> Although this version there are many functional improvements, but it is recommended that users upgrade to version 6.0, 6.0, 26 has released the first version, and now is very stable and has a good performance. </p><p> Details on the Tomcat 5.5.29 version of the improved content see <a href=\"http://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-5.5-doc/changelog.html\" target=\"_blank\">ChangeLog</a> . </p><p> <a href=\"http://tomcat.apache.org/download-55.cgi\" target=\"_blank\">Download Tomcat5.5.29</a> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','Tomcat 5.5 is an older version, just released 5.5.29 version mainly fixes some serious bug, but also to upgrade a number of Java class libraries, such as commons-pool and so on.  Although this version there are many functional improvements, but it is recommended that users upgrade to version 6.0,...'),(135,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0430/88.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Looking for open source enterprise: the enterprise open source company Red Hat','Looking_for_open_source_enterprise_the_enterprise_open_source_company_Red_Hat','2010-04-30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> As the world\'s leading open source and Linux provider, Red Hat Software\'s corporate culture and the &quot;open, free, collaboration,&quot; has a natural kinship, HR is the most expected this concept to the limits. </p><p> Red Hat Beijing office lounge in the pool table, Zheng Yan dubbed by the Office of the busiest table. In addition to writing the code in the gap for those who break the engineers responsible for Greater China and Australia, Zheng Yan, senior recruiting manager will own or even after lunch marked the two Councils. Today, free and open corporate culture more and more present in the enterprise, but Red Hat\'s culture is more prominent. As the most revolutionary technology of the company, Red Hat software product itself for such a unique corporate culture of dedication. </p><p> &quot;At first I did not understand Red Hat\'s open source is, but I was digging around the search is very professional, he told me, the future must be open source world, the world\'s best engineers so much doing in this product contribution, and our code is free to use for the community. &quot;joining the company, Zheng Yan more convinced their judgments. As the financial crisis, many companies have reduced revenue, and Red Hat in the world all achieve a contrarian uplink. </p><p> In China, the report also reflected the beautiful changes in the organization, from the beginning of this year, Red Hat to Beijing looking for new office, because this year the company\'s development plans and last year just as quickly. In fact, in that room with pool tables in the lounge, the walls continued with new recruits Post self-introduction, and this one, many people are attracted to Red Hat\'s campus presentation. </p><p> <strong>Flexible Culture</strong> </p><p> End of last year\'s campus recruitment propaganda, Zheng Yan\'s style and very different from other HR companies. Traditionally, such propaganda in the strict sense should be wearing suits, and Zheng Yan was wearing boots and denim shorts, and her cool short hair style, it is added to this alternative points. </p><p> &quot;HR on behalf of the company\'s corporate culture, is a candidate to understand the company\'s bridge, the day I am also very active on stage, I move around, jump, and students interaction, joking. And we preach the process, to take a very variety of forms, including a video, is the company\'s own making, the topic is the performance of our daily working conditions, this casual and very attractive short positive students. &quot; </p><p> Now more and more young people with personality, how to meet them? Zheng Yanxi hope this message is Red Hat\'s free and open spirit. Many of my colleagues as the company needs to report directly to the United States, so sometimes you will work, meetings late into the night, and many colleagues hope to have the time to write code more quiet work space, the company respect the work habits of employees, staff believed arranged for independent work time, so Red Hat is not used flexible working time system. </p><p> Zheng Yan themselves are the direct beneficiaries of this work system. As a child is just 1 year old new mother, at first, her friends around to the Red Hat development rather puzzled. For a career woman, in order to balance work and life, such moments are usually more suitable for Enron in the original live enterprise Moreover, Zheng Yan, she has worked for a company in the last 4 years and outstanding performance. </p><p> After the Red Hat, Zheng Yan of the great pressure of work, but she still can arrange your own pace, and working hours. &quot;Red Hat is a user-friendly and encourage the personal development of the company, our culture is the most important freedom, because open source is free, this freedom is based on trust, which also reflects the company\'s employees respect. My house from the company very far, but I can choose to stagger the rush hour, so that flexible working for me to win a higher efficiency, but also can arrange a good family life. &quot; </p><p> Open and free culture is reflected in many ways, the flexible working time management is a human performance. In addition, the company will arrange special staff for everyone to buy their favorite snacks, beverages, for staff to provide quality meals. This culture is indeed a truly effective the favorite to win the staff, although the average age of Red Hat employees only 26 years old, but the turnover rate of businesses remain low at below 5%, which is rare in the IT industry, Moreover, Red Hat is not completely rely on the kind of salaries to keep people in the management system. </p><p> <strong>Within the recommended optimal</strong> </p><p> And corporate values to keep the same people, the source of recruitment is the choice of candidates. For in July 2009 had just joined the Red Hat software Yan Zheng, initially invited her to the company rather puzzled. Because that time period, we more or talking about the financial crisis, most companies have a hiring freeze, and she has work to do a recruitment focus for the HR person in charge. </p><p> And Red Hat\'s recent efforts to recruit and the past is entirely different. Zheng Yan in the year before the company, Red Hat not only recruited 20 people, and she came after six months, has reached 40 people. To attract more outstanding personnel, in addition to the number of jobs, even before the problem difficult to solve the graduate account, Zheng Yan fundamental for the company through the multi-mediation resolved. </p><p> In addition to graduates, the company now more than ever, attention to the recommendation of internal talent. In Zhengyan Gang joined the company when the internal referral system has been started, and the company also provides a high for this budget. Now from the company headquarters to China, we hope to dig more deeply this project, for which Red Hat in the global selection of some wonderful HR to join the project, Zheng Yan is one of the member. </p><p> Optimized internal referral system is more rigorous than ever before, and humane. The key is, the company hopes will be in the previous Red Hat Enterprise culture to candidates, in order to improve the success rate of this project. As employees of Red Hat in the past often only published in a number of industry forums employment needs of their company, and most of the resume is given the staff and Red Hat is not met, so the past success of Red Hat\'s recommended rate of zero. Today, the project carried out soon, already have three colleagues through the way of success within the recommended joining Red Hat. </p><p> &quot;In the past only screening employees, and now we ask to interview each other, thus improving the success rate, but also allow a better understanding of the new employees joining the likes of Red Hat\'s culture, so although the recent time, we increased the number of recruitment Many, but not dilute our culture. &quot; </p><p> Within the recommended approach has been the HR technology companies favored by natural cost advantage is one of the reasons this project to deepen, but the traditional recruitment channels, Red Hat still has not given up. Zheng Yan to the company, will be invited each of the company\'s service provider negotiations and the formation of competition between them to quickly improve the service level of service. When the search firm candidates fail to provide Red Hat requirements, Zheng Yan, and their detailed analysis will be the reason, once again clarify the job requirements, to understand the business as much as possible the intention of the other party to continue to promote their service. </p><p> Zheng Yan\'s efforts to get the company\'s identity, his boss, the boss of the region are working for her efficiency and performance that surprises. Zheng Yan to feel proud of their business also includes the recognition of her head, because the rapid expansion of business, R &amp; D centers in China, general manager of one of the things that most worried the rapid establishment of the team, and Zheng Yan just help to him. </p><p> &quot;I believe the next 5 to 10 years, China\'s HR recruitment is still dominated, because the business managers, HR to help them the most, and most obvious is the recruitment, finding the right person to build a good team, which only after we talk about talent management and business development. &quot; </p><p> <strong>Of boss</strong> </p><p> However, Yan Zheng clearer that, as HR, is not to find the right employees to the company even if successful, it is important also to obtain the trust of leaders of HR, trust comes from the professionalism and good communication, has been for 12 years Yan Zheng recruiting experience, she\'s a very deep understanding of this trust. </p><p> &quot;At this point, I am very grateful to the original company, because where I need to handle larger volumes of recruitment, personnel need to be more diversified, which I accumulated a lot of experience.&quot; Which is a very important one and owner communication. </p><p> Professional competence required of employers in Red Hat, Zheng Yan received the greatest support for his boss. This is one of the most obvious is the boss of her trust. As the boss\'s office office in the United States, so far, Zheng Yan, and the boss has no chance to really meet up. &quot;But my boss is very good character, and she do things cleanly, my personality is also very direct, so the communication between us is very smooth. I soon after taking office, we exchanged pictures. When I select local Chinese excellent service, looking for her approval of some projects, she is very fast to me feedback, as long as I made clear reason, she would say, \'I think you must be the best choice.\' &quot; </p><p> In addition to the support of the work, there are quite a lot of things to Zheng Yan moved. Due to time differences, in the past, Zheng Yan needs about 3 times a week, and headquarters in the evening to meet the various project departments, because the more the project leader in the United States or Europe, Zheng Yan to adapt to most of their working time. And once in a meeting and his boss, the other heard the sound of crying children Zheng Yan, the boss immediately said after the meeting, be sure to Zheng Yan of the day, but their choice in the evening. &quot;I believe it is the management of human, so I have a driving force even more. In fact, this is where Red Hat\'s culture.&quot; </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>',' As the world\'s leading open source and Linux provider, Red Hat Software\'s corporate culture and the \"open, free, collaboration,\" has a natural kinship, HR is the most expected this concept to the limits.  Red Hat Beijing office lounge in the pool table, Zheng Yan dubbed by the Office of the...'),(136,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0828/564.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Edge network - Webmaster Overview','Edge_network__Webmaster_Overview','2010-08-28','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p><table border=\"0\" width=\"607\"><tbody><tr><td><div> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"276\" onclick=\"window.open(&apos;/uploads/allimg/100718/1_100718021451_1.png&apos;)\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.net/uploads/allimg/100718/1_100718023605_1.png\" style=\"width: 151px; height: 202px; cursor: pointer\" width=\"205\" /></span></span> </div></td><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">High Junfeng, net name: South African Ant</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Xidian University, graduating with the system architect / Oracle DBA.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linux open source enthusiasts, database enthusiasts.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Has been committed with the Linux operating system, Oracle database management p optimization field, now principally engaged in web-based system architecture design and network operation and maintenance, good open-source Linux applications, systems management, performance optimization, oracle database, troubleshooting, performance tuning there is a certain studies.</span></span> </p></td></tr></tbody></table></p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">8 years experience in Linux system administration and maintenance of more than 5 years experience with oracle database</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Served with a large foreign telecommunications equipment suppliers, is responsible for China Mobile and oracle database backend unix system normal operation, currently working in the domestic well-known e-government enterprise, planning and design and maintain the country\'s 10 provincial-level e-government system a few.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><br /> <font color=\"#256eb1\"><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/2010/0507/98.html\" target=\"_blank\">Individual monograph published in 2010 &quot;Linux the essence of enterprise applications,&quot;</a></font> <br /> <a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/linux/2010/0421/10.html\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#256eb1\">Individual monograph published in 2009 &quot;step by step Linux&quot;</font></a> <br /> 2007 Technical Excellence Award winner IXPUB IT168 Linux Forum Moderator plate</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">You can contact the webmaster as follows:</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">MSN: <a href=\"mailto:gaojf_888@hotmail.com\"><font color=\"#256eb1\">gaojf_888@hotmail.com</font></a></span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">QQ: 397824870</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Email: dba.gao @ gmail.com</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Can also site a message, I will reply to you within the first time!</span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','High Junfeng, net name: South African AntXidian University, graduating with the system architect / Oracle DBA.Linux open source enthusiasts, database enthusiasts.Has been committed with the Linux operating system, Oracle database management p optimization field, now principally engaged in web-based...'),(137,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0711/316.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Domestic open source software company Red Flag 2000, CEOs were','Domestic_open_source_software_company_Red_Flag_2000_CEOs_were','2010-07-11','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <strong>Red Flag 2000 out of office software</strong> </p><p> Insider sources, early May, &quot;Nuclear high base&quot; project-based software testing has been completed. In the office area, Kingsoft office software products ranked first, Evermore Office subordination, both of which were obtained 50 million ~ 60 million of central government funding. The Red Flag 2000 office software product is definitely out, because of its so-called open-source office software products are not made with completely independent intellectual property rights of real domestic product. </p><p> Yuan Meng introduced red RedOffice office 2000 software products owned by over 90% of software code to copy the open source OpenOffice. Red flag on the surface of 2000 added a shell, which claimed 100% of the independent intellectual property rights, and changed its name from the OpenOffice RedOffice, traces directly to the elimination of open source products. </p><p> OpenOffice open source office software was first developed for a German company, later acquired by the U.S. Sun. Sun has now merged with Oracle, its intellectual property rights belonging to Oracle. </p><p> In the &quot;nuclear high base&quot; project-based software testing, the Red Flag 2000 RedOffice winning software and office software products because the &quot;non-domestic&quot; and is blocked at the door, dragged a red flag in 2000 the company directly. </p><p> The insider said the better things in the open source software, &quot;fifth&quot; period, the CAS software investment 30% owned by Red Flag Software, a Hong Kong investment company called the Chinese 70% in 2000, the Chinese joint venture company in 2000, before Hu Yong president. Yong Hu was later combined in a joint venture enterprise set up a red 2000 power, power is the controlling shareholder in the enterprise. Red Flag 2000, the goal is to RedOffice office software applications for state financial support. </p><p> It is understood the company\'s working capital difficult to sustain the funding to other countries. Funding can not come now, the shareholders of the investment will boondoggle. </p><p> Alleged, when the red flag will be invested in power prices in 2000, is made of the value of their products will be supported by the State, but now found that &quot;domestic&quot; is a farce, so the recent Red Flag 2000, a major shareholder in power eliminates the red flag 2000 rate Yong Hu, general manager duties only. </p><p> When this reporter interviewed the red flag in 2000, the company\'s brand in this part of the Department of a dedicated staff of content distribution does not deny this, saying only that &quot;there is no clear message in this regard can be made public.&quot; </p><p> <strong>Universal South is also false?</strong> </p><p> Yuan Meng said the Chinese IT circles nowadays from a local copy or other open source products and packaging to 100% independent intellectual property products, and then apply for grants to state examples of particularly high. </p><p> Insider sources, the South is another common example. </p><p> GM recently held in the South of product release, the company\'s main database product GBase8g product development background in the phrase: &quot;Universal Data Technology Co., Ltd. Tianjin, Nanjing University and a research institute cooperation, joint research and data technology, Nankai University, Jilin University Department of scientific research database ... .... &quot; But the reporters call the Nankai University and Jilin University, all told, these two institutions did not exist. </p><p> For the company claims its database products with independent intellectual property rights GBase8g, Yuan Meng pointed out that the product claims to support Windows platform, which is obvious flaws. According to him, nowadays the major database products are built on open architecture, based on only a small database will support Windows platforms, GBase8g database is a large database of products, said, &quot;support the Windows platform&quot;, it is certainly false. </p><p> &quot;Daily Economic News&quot; interviewed GM CEO Liu Bo South. Data on the company and the Nankai Institute of Technology, Jilin University, Department of Technical Cooperation of the things the database, Liu Bo said he was half-way into this company, and therefore it is not clear. &quot;South Common database products developed technical architecture is the new architecture, and Oracle and other database technology architecture is completely different.&quot; Liu Bo said some people raised objections to the company\'s product technology, this is not a bad thing, you can sit down communication. </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','Red Flag 2000 out of office software Insider sources, early May, \"Nuclear high base\" project-based software testing has been completed. In the office area, Kingsoft office software products ranked first, Evermore Office subordination, both of which were obtained 50 million ~ 60 million of central...'),(138,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0812/439.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Linux or Windows server systems, the use of who we are in the end','Linux_or_Windows_server_systems_the_use_of_who_we_are_in_the_end','2010-08-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">What do you think of a better server operating system is Microsoft\'s Windows or open-source Linux? On this issue gave rise to numerous debates, but a long time Windows and Linux, used by IT consultants say, to say which server operating system best work to hard to answer, because in the choice of server operating system, we need to combine cost, performance, security and applications considered.</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Select the reason Linux operating system</span></span></strong> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">SystemExperts chief adviser Phil Cox said: &quot;The use of Linux, the operating system can not spend money, but if you choose Windows, are required to pay licensing fees to Microsoft, so from a cost considerations, Linux is the best choice, and in any physical hardware platform, Linux is always showing the performance of about 25% faster. &quot;</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Linux is also more flexible to use, free, and even the kernel can make changes to, a lot of customization settings in Windows, is not experience, so there are too many people praising Linux, but something always has two sides, Cox pointed out, is Because Linux is flexible, making maintenance more difficult, leading to many business users prohibitive.</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">For example, Linux kernel can be modified and highly customized, so the IT staff have higher skill requirements, the other, Linux versions of many application compatibility issues often all kinds of weird.</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Select the reason Windows operating system</span></span></strong> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Windows attraction is stable, although less flexible, but in the integration of applications, Windows is often the most simple. And Microsoft executives said: The future of server operating system will have great movement.</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">In addition, Windows itself comes with a good access control mechanisms need to install any plug-ins or patches can achieve effective access control.</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Either Windows or Linux, system patch exists, but to the Windows patching is much easier, and all patches are from Microsoft. Patch mechanism under which Linux is more complicated, a software development organization released a patch for a single software, Linux distribution vendors have released a collection of patches, while Linux is a patch under the high-risk thing. Although Linux, patching some difficulties, but in the powerful open source software in several very strong patch management tools. In short, the patch to the Linux system is a very complicated matter, not a bit daring and is not easily grasp the patches, and in Windows, even if it was new to the line started going to sit back and relax in to the system can also install the patch.</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Cox said: &quot;Linux community does not TechNet, Linux users must seek the help of the community, and as such, Linux community will be so prosperous.&quot;</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Perhaps it is for these reasons that has caused everyone to say that Linux is good, yet you dare not, otherwise why continue to occupy most of the Windows enterprise server? Some vertical industries, but now began to favor Linux, and Linux as the financial industry has become the largest user.</span></span> </p><p class=\"newtext\"> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Cox said that Linux and open source software applications in the enterprise extranet is still very common, and the other, Linux is loved in the field of industrial technology, we have many products and services can see the shadow of Linux, such as Amazon\'s EC2 cloud computing data center is built on top of Xen\'s Linux server.</span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','What do you think of a better server operating system is Microsoft\'s Windows or open-source Linux? On this issue gave rise to numerous debates, but a long time Windows and Linux, used by IT consultants say, to say which server operating system best work to hard to answer, because in the choice of...');
INSERT INTO `entries` VALUES (139,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0722/341.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Oracle Mysql and java development after the acquisition will be better','Oracle_Mysql_and_java_development_after_the_acquisition_will_be_better','2010-07-22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> A few days ago to see a lot of people buy SUN oracle all the talk after, everyone was very worried about mysql and java will be taken for granted that the MySQL and Java is about to face this experience. <br /> However, according to Jaspersoft survey of developers, after the Oracle acquisition of SUN, MySQL, Java has not been much impact, in fact, the development of both better than before. <br /> The following are the survey of some interesting conclusions: </p><p><br /> Ã¢Â€Â¢ More than 75% of people think that under the impetus of MySQL in Oracle will maintain the status quo or better <br /> Ã¢Â€Â¢ More than 75% of people think that the development of MySQL will remain the same pace or faster <br /> Ã¢Â€Â¢ Almost all developers participating in the survey said they would continue to use the Java <br /><br /> Ã¢Â€Â¢ Nearly 80% of people think that Java Community Process (JCP) will remain the same or better development </p><p><br /> The findings on the Java not a surprise, because otherwise no better choice. And although there are many other open source database, but most developers still prefer to use MySQL, they also believe that Oracle will maintain the sustainable development of MySQL. <br /> In any case, the future of MySQL and Java compare with OpenSolaris is not appropriate, because both use the very broad, to give them to give up most of the users. <br /></p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>',' A few days ago to see a lot of people buy SUN oracle all the talk after, everyone was very worried about mysql and java will be taken for granted that the MySQL and Java is about to face this experience.  However, according to Jaspersoft survey of developers, after the Oracle acquisition of SUN,...'),(140,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0719/326.html','http://www.ixdba.net','OpenSolaris is facing the disintegration of the Commission?','OpenSolaris_is_facing_the_disintegration_of_the_Commission','2010-07-19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> SUN OpenSolaris is a company (now acquired by Oracle) initiated by the open source operating system project to build the Solaris operating system-based developer community for the project was mainly targeted at developers (that is, software design , computer programmer), system administrator (Information Management Division, Information Management Division, Information Management staff) and the user (users), who expect to make Solaris through the further development and enhancement. <br /> Recently, foreign media reports, the Commission is currently faced with the dissolution of OpenSolaris crisis. After the Oracle acquisition of Sun, OpenSolaris is easy to face the problem of the main transition. Currently OpenSolaris Commission (OGB) has issued an ultimatum to the Oracle, Oracle hopes before the Aug. 16 to appoint a contact person to participate in decision-making OpenSolaris. Otherwise OpenSolaris Management Committee will be dissolved or transferred to Oracle to manage themselves. <br /> The provisions of Articles in the OpenSolaris OGB must be composed of three administrators, one of whom must be a member of their company as, and now the situation is less than 3 members, which will also lead to the disintegration of OGB. From the beginning of this year in February, OpenSolaris community and the relationship between Oracle is very tense, which also led to neglect of the Oracle communication links with the communities. <br /> Former Oracle vice president and chief officer Jeb Dabsteel said users will attend OGB held in the July 11 meeting, but reports said he did not attend that day and did not make any explanation. OGB can do is now resigned to refuse cooperation with Oracle. <br /> It is said that, Sun Open Source Advocacy Officer Simon Phipps before the 11th General Assembly on OGB said, OpenSolaris can not be established between the community and Oracle working together. In his view, there is now the community has lost the value of target. <br /> Oracle in the end, how would the relationship between treatment and OGB, OGB Do you really want to face the disintegration? <br /></p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>',' SUN OpenSolaris is a company (now acquired by Oracle) initiated by the open source operating system project to build the Solaris operating system-based developer community for the project was mainly targeted at developers (that is, software design , computer programmer), system administrator...'),(141,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/0711/313.html','http://www.ixdba.net','50 most intelligent global technology executives: Ma list','50_most_intelligent_global_technology_executives_Ma_list','2010-07-11','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> According to foreign media reports, the &quot;Fortune&quot; magazine online edition of the global technology markets on Friday named its 50 top executives the most intelligent, Apple CEO Steve Jobs (Steve Jobs) and Alibaba CEO Jack Ma, etc. the list. </p><div class=\"NewsContent TextContent\" id=\"OSChina_News_10419\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/100711/1RRRH6-0.png\" style=\"float: right; margin: 0px 0px 10px 10px\" /></div><p> &quot;Fortune&quot; magazine list of the 50 top executives were subdivided, respectively, the smartest named its CEO, the most intelligent designer, the most intelligent analyst, founder of the most intelligent, most intelligent engineers, the most intelligent scientists, inventor of the most intelligent, most intelligent and most intelligent scientists and other senior management personnel. </p><p> <strong>The following is the &quot;wealth&quot; area of the Top 50 global technology smartest executives:<