S\">(Shared Pool)</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">-</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Tai Chi <span lang=\"EN-US\">(Large Pool)</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">- Java</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">pool <span lang=\"EN-US\">(Java Pool)</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\">Y: Arial &quot;&gt; - <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Streams pool <span lang=\"EN-US\">(Streams Pool --- 10g</span> later only) <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">-</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Redo log buffer <span lang=\"EN-US\">(Redo Log Buffer)</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">-</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Other <span lang=\"EN-US\">buffer caches</span> (such as <span lang=\"EN-US\">KEEP, RECYCLE, and other block sizes cache,</span> etc.) <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">- Fixed SGA and other internal <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">allocations.</span></span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><spa