pecial-character: line-break\" /></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 20.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"> <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">A. SQL</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">statements on the table above together with the row-level <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">locks,</span> confirmation is <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">completed,</span> must be added the command</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">COMMIT</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">transaction processing to the end of the entry into <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">force,</span> otherwise the change is not necessarily written to the <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">database.</span> If you wish to withdraw these <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">operations,</span></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">you</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">can use the command</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">ROLLBACK <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">recovery.</span> <br /><br /> B.</span></strong><html> na &quot;&gt; running <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">INSERT,</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">DELETE,</span> and</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">UPDATE</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">statements may be operating before the best estimate for the range of <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">records,</span> it should be limited to small <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">(a</span> million <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">records) range.</span> or use</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">ORACLE</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">great deal of things back back <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">section.</span> program responds to slow or even <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">unresponsive.</span> If the number of records on hundreds of thousands of these <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">operations,</span> these</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">SQL</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">statements can be sub-sub-sub-complete</span></strong>Y: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma &quot;&gt;, <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">during which confirm things with</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">COMMIT <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993300; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">processing.</span></span></strong> </p>','1.INSERT (insert records into the data table statement) INSERT INTO table (field name 1, field name 2, ... ...) VALUES (value 1, value 2, ... ...);  INSERT INTO table (field name 1, field name 2, ... ...) SELECT (field name 1, field name 2, ... ...) FROM another table; IXDBA.NET Technical Community...'),(236,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/33/2011.html','http://www.ixdba.net','oracle daily operations summary: Table space articles','oracle_daily_operations_summary_Table_space_articles','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<html><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">1.create tablespaces</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">(create</span> table <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">space)</span></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">sql&gt; <span style=\"COLOR: #333399\"><strong>create tablespace tablespace_name datafile \'c: \\ oracle \\ oradata \\ file1.dbf\' size 100m