 <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: \'MS Shell Dlg\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">Checkpoint can cause the occurrence of</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: \'MS Shell Dlg\'\"></span></strong> </p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 20.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"> <strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">Note: If a simple</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">offline</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">datafile,</span> it will not trigger the checkpoint file, only the time for the</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">offline tablespace</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">files will trigger the checkpoint, which is why</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">online datafile</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #993366; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; F