-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">*</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.0pt\">Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â  </span>-Hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt &quot;&gt; If the table already has primary key or unique index on non-null value, <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">add</span> to the <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">redo</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">log information will be minimal.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">*</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.0pt\">Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â Ã‚Â  </span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.