ss=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\">archival mode.</font></font></font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">Ã‚Â </span></font></font></font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Ã‚Â </font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\">Solution Description:</font></font></font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\">=====================</font></font></font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">Ã‚Â </span></font></font></font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\">In general, the stale status of a redo log member should not be a cause for</font></font></font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\">great concern, unless you observe that this happens frequently or</font></font></font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\">systematic</font></font></font></span><html> ally. <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">Ã‚Â  </span> Keep in mind that a stale log is not necessarily an invalid </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">log, but more of an &quot;in-doubt&quot; one. Once the corresponding redo group becomes</span></font></font></font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"BACKGROUND: #cccccc; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">the current one again, the stale status will go away by itself.</span></font></font></font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Ã‚Â </font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Ã‚Â </font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Here is an example:</font></span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"></span></font> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Ã‚Â </font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"