COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">example:</font></span> <br /> SELECT operation, sql_redo, sql_undo FROM V $ logmnr_contents <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">Ã‚Â  </span> WHERE seg_name = \'QIUYB\'; <br /><br /> OPERATION SQL_REDO SQL_UNDO <br /> ---------- -------------------------- -------------- ------------ <br /> INSERT inser into qiuyb.qiuyb ... delete from qiuyb.qiuyb ... <br /><br /></span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">One</font></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">operation</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">that is <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">operating,</span> sql_redo refers to the actual <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">operation,</span> sql_undo mean the opposite for the abolition of the operation.</font></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\"><br /><br /></span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">b,</span> view the</font></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">DDL <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">operation,</font></span> for <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">example:</font></span> <br /> SELECT timstamp, <br /> sql_redo <br /> FROM v $ logmnr_contents <br /> WHERE upper (sql_redo) like \'% TRUNCATE%\';</span> </p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">7,</span> the end of</font></span>dana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma &quot;&gt; LogMiner <font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">analysis.</span></font> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\"><br /> SQL&gt; BEGIN <br /> 2 dbms_logmnr.end_logmnr; <br /> 3 end; <br /> 4 /</span> </p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"> <strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">Third, the data associated with the</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">LogMiner</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">dictionary.</span></strong> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\"><br /></span> <font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">1,</span> v</span></font> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">$ loglist</span> <font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">It is used to display some information about the history log file</span></font> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\"><br /></span> <font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">2,</span> v</span></font> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">$ logmnr_dictionary</span> <font face=\"Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">for</span><