dana\">3)</span> to optimize the disk (including the file system), increased</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\">I / O</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">throughput;</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\">4)</span> network bandwidth;</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\">Ã‚Â </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\">2,</span> general factors that affect system performance:</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">1)</span> CPU</span> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\">2)</span> memory</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0c