ed books, mainly about the basic theory and basic commands, such as: &quot; <a class=\"kw\" href=\"/article/d4/444.html\">Linux</a> based &quot;,&quot; Redhat 9.0 system administrator complete study guide &quot;; or download some basic information. System to read a book, and in the linux system (you can install a virtual machine with vmware) to practice the basic commands. (The reason why Linux from the beginning, because relative to other unix systems, Linux is relatively simple or easy entry)</font> </p><p> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><strong>2. Configure the server</strong></font></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Can try to configure a web server or FTP server or mail server (sendmail) or other application servers such as: vpn (pptp or ipsec). Do not just start configuring the pursuit of perfection, as long as you can to achieve basic functionality. This part of the book is basically copying the steps can be realized.</font> </p><p> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><strong>3. Software installation and server management</strong></font></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Can try to install some source program (do not use the rpm package installation, or install the program with the installation), through the. / Configure make make install Compile and other steps to master the program and the installation method. Day to day management control of both the Linux server methods: such as log management, process management, backup and recovery methods, user management, privilege management, etc., basically become a Linux system administrator. Usually the technical aspects of multi-access linux website or forum may also increase your skills and experience.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Note: Many people learn or use Linux for many years, but the level just to stay here</font> </p><p> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><strong>4. Replacement of thinking</strong></font></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">If the system to learn the basic knowledge of linux and simply configure some application servers, and master the basic usage of the command, then need to be replaced Synovate, learn about the Linux architecture knowledge and understanding of Linux system architecture, such as What role etc directory is / usr / bin / usr / spool / var / opt is what role, ext3 file system, what features and more. Different view from Synovate on Linux systems. At the same time you can try to compile the kernel, and familiar with the kernel modules, through the knowledge of the kernel, allowing you to understand some of the core linux technology.</font> </p><p> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><strong>5. Learn other unix systems</strong></font></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">If you are basically familiar with the Linux system, now can learn the other systems, such as: Solaris, AIX, BSD ... ... ... ... and so, after all, many important servers are not Linux. Many systems can be installed in a virtual machine, such as the installation of a Solaris x86 virtual machine or virtual machine from the Internet or the SCO ... ... ... ... in a virtual machine on a systematic study of the system, familiar with its architecture, and compare with Linux there different. For some special systems, online testing machines are also good people of information released, you can remotely log on to learn (do not delete files or damage yo.) Other systems in the learning process, can access the BBS forum for related systems, look at other people\'s problem is how to solve. If you are familiar with Linux, learn other unix system should be fast. Of course, if your company has some servers, such as: SUN880 or HP server or IBM servers, you should soon be able to be experienced solaris / HP-UNIX / AIX master.</font> </p><p> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><strong>6. To learn shell programming</strong></font></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">As a real good unix system administrator, do not know shell programming is absolutely impossible (note the absolute), because the unix system, many shell scripts, shell programming techniques mastered, you can thoroughly understand the unix system to the operation of the program. But also for unix systems, many system administration can write shell scripts to implement, such as automatic backup, automatically check the network disconnection concurrent mail notification, automatically checks the VPN status, PPTP users to dial-in information collection and more. Proficient in shell programming, let you easily manage and control a flexible Unix systems.</font> </p><p> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><strong>7. Learning C Programming</strong></font></font> </p> <font color=\"#ecf4f5\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"><a href=\"http://bbs.ixdba.net\"><strong>IXDBA.NET Community Forums</strong></a></font> <br /><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">This step I do not say, after all, to achieve this level of unix system administration rarely (except developers). Many of the Unix program written by C, control programming, you can write an application under unix.</font> </p><p> <font size=\"2\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><strong>8. Make your own unix distributions</strong></font></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">If the Linux kernel to compile, program cuts, system optimization, you can make their own unix system. Linux distributions like too much now, but they are Linux kernel, file system organization is not the same as it. We can not produce a single person like Redhat or debian like system, but can make small, dedicated systems, such as making a dedicated web server or a dedicated gateway firewall system.</font> </p>','I remember I wrote a previous entry unix article, here is how to become a unix expert articles, personal little more experience, we welcome...'),(281,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/90/448.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Novice strongly recommended: linux 