as now become (ORCL) the letter of the wound. In fact, the reason why the EU has been reluctant to approve the acquisition of $ 5,600,000,000 Oracle SUN (JAVA) transactions, the existence of this thorn in the side is a key reason. <br /><br /> While Oracle has repeatedly argued, but the EU remains convinced, will also recruit\'s MySQL, Oracle will mean more powerful, making the database contrary to fair competition in the market. Prior to this, the U.S. Justice Department expressed no objection to the approval of the transaction. <br /><br /> Oracle in a report Monday afternoon that &quot;the EU statement of objections shows that they are competitive and open source database development are two sides to understand there is a significant deviation.&quot; <br /><br /> Struggle in the end <br /><br /> To Oracle CEO Larry Ellison (Larry Ellison) and his company to change course, and now the possibility seems extremely limited, they would be difficult to make such concessions like MySQL split stance. <br /><br /> Ingres is second only to Red Hat (RHT) in the second-largest open source company, the CEO blog Hart (Roger Burkhardt) said, &quot;I have many colleagues who have worked with Larry Ellison, they are estimated He will fight in the end. &quot; <br /><br /> However, this really is the most sensible choice? In fact, even Ellison himself emphasized, the transaction can only delay the loss of SUN increasing. SUN on Friday reported a first quarter, the company revenue over the same period the previous fiscal year fell 25% as much as losses. <br /><br /> The reason why Oracle would consider hard-line stance, perhaps because more than once before tasted the sweetness of sake. After all, the Oracle acquisition of PeopleSoft business application software developer, when the Ministry of Justice have also been such a battle, Oracle, or the upper hand eventually succeeded in 2004, 10.3 billion acquisition of PeopleSoft. <br /><br /> According to former colleagues say, Ellison fond of &quot;The Art of War&quot;, he may now be browsing this ancient Chinese military classics, looking for ways to face the issues at hand. <br /><br /> The Art of War <br /><br /> If Ellison is studying the &quot;Art of War&quot;, he noted that there should be a very important concept, that is not easily damaged targets, or the enemy. <br /><br /> The great military strategist, wrote, &quot;Where the military forces of the law, the country is on the second break the country; army is on breaking the military, followed by; brigade is on; breaking tour followed; death is on the whole, breaking Death second; the whole Wu is on break, followed by Wu. &quot; <br /><br /> In fact, the problem is that how important for Oracle, MySQL. Oracle is worth its weight with the European Union protracted course of time the war? You know, this war will inevitably further damage SUN, to its rivals IBM Corp. (IBM) and Hewlett-Packard (HPQ) to provide fish in troubled waters, the chance to steal customers. Or, they should be split out of MySQL, in order to obtain better results have the first bit of damage? <br /><br /> Think20/20 Research analyst Winter (Heath Winter) I believe, MySQL Oracle is not worth a fight. <br /><br /> Winter said, &quot;It appears that Oracle really is not worth the important goal is not to pay too much.&quot; Although not openly MySQL SUN specific revenue, but the Winter estimates, and their 300 million in annual revenue will dollars, and may even have to come lower. In fact, MySQL was acquired in January 2008, and their revenues in 2007 but only $ 50,000,000. <br /><br /> &quot;For this you can choose to give up an important deal?&quot; <br /><br /> Supporters of MySQL made some conspiracy theory, they believe, Ellison is to buy the company to ruin, because he was afraid of the latter into a potentially serious threat to Oracle. But at the moment, MySQL seems to be limited influence of small and medium enterprises, start-up company, or Web 2.0 circles, among the entire database market, their position really is not worth mentioning. <br /><br /> In the European market, their position is even more pitiful. According to Gartner Inc. 2008 data, Oracle Europe and the Middle East has about 50% market share, and in the total size of USD 4.8 billion on a huge cake, MySQL enjoy only a small 0.04%. However, the EU is mainly concerned with too much pricing power of Oracle. <br /><br /> In fact, from the day on SUN acquired MySQL, they already face a number of potential threat. MySQL co-founder Wade Corners (Michael Widenius) has left the SUN, is another company called MariaDB database, which to some extent, can also be counted as a successor to MySQL.</font>','empty\n'),(337,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/41/2136.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Ubuntu 9.10 officially released, Linux enthusiasts of the Gospel','Ubuntu_910_officially_released_Linux_enthusiasts_of_the_Gospel','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">The Ubuntu9.10 operating system code-named KarmicKoala schedule released today and on-line, to the Linux system once again offer fans a feast.</font> <p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Ubuntu9.10 very many new features, such as:</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">- Re-design, faster, more energetic startup and logon interface experience</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">- Optimized audio framework (can be as Vista/Win7 multiple applications as a separate volume control)</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">- Improving the 3G wireless broadband connectivity</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">- New version of the Software Center (SoftwareCenter)</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">- To provide a paper backup, sync and sharing of online services UbuntuOne</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">-Firefox3.5 Browser</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">-OpenOffice.org3.0 office suite</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">-F-Spot photo management software</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Ubuntu9.10 support 25 international languages, including Chinese translations of 90%, 80% degree of Traditional Chinese translation, and other 9 languages under consideration.</font> </p><p style=\"MARGIN: 6px 3px 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 30px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Ubuntu9.10 continue to provide desktop, Internet edition, the server version of the three versions, as well as Kubuntu, Edubuntu and other derivative versions are provided free of charge, you can download the installation ISO image, or apply for a CD / DVD installation disc.</font> </p>','Ubuntu9.10 very many new features, such...'),(338,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/03/2135.html','http://www.ixdba.net','John Chuang RedHat push virtualization virtualization management software market','John_Chuang_RedHat_push_virtualization_virtualization_management_software_market','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Red Hat\'s enterprise-class server virtualization products will support Linux and Windows virtual servers and desktops. <br /><br /> Commitment to Red Hat on Tuesday said it would provide a separate management procedures and management tools, and preparing to go top with VMware and Microsoft virtualization and cloud computing infrastructure providers to compete. <br /><br /> This enterprise-class Red Hat\'s virtualization software can be deployed on any server, including a standalone hypervisor and virtualization management of Red Hat Enterprise platform. Both are Red Hat summit in August this year, first introduced above. <br /><br /> Has 12 major application with Windows, Linux and Apple Mac systems to establish a connection. <br /><br /> Red Hat Enterprise Virtualization Manager supports both Linux and Windows virtual servers and desktops. Management program is based on Red Hat Enterprise 5.4 kernel and KVM, which is published earlier this year, Red Hat version. <br /><br /> &quot;It inherits all the enterprise features of RHEL 5,&quot; Red Hat virtualization Navin Thadani, senior director of operations said. <br /><br /> Red Hat Enterprise Virtualization Manager (Enterprise Virtualization Hypervisor) within the host can be extended to 96 cores and 1TB of memory, customers can get 16 CPU and 64GB of virtual memory. In addition, it also supports live migration, power management, multi-port I / O and memory page sharing. <br /><br /> Red Hat Enterprise Virtualization Manager (Enterprise Virtualization Manager) is the server, the second part of the package. It is a centralized management system server virtualization with high availability tools, real-time migration, load balancing and image management, currently supports Linux and Windows systems. Of course, it also has a monitoring tool. <br /><br /> Red Hat also said it is testing Red Hat Enterprise Virtualization Manager desktop version, desktop version will provide a complete VDI environment and the SPICE remote rendering technology support. <br /><br /> These tools are 107 million last year, the Red Hat acquisition of Qumranet\'s products. Red Hat in September of this year, these tools into the libvirt API, the current API of virtualization products are used by Red Hat. Some time ago Red Hat announced the official RHEL 6, and that these tools will work with VMware, to cooperate on the basis of management platform, which the partners will be required in the base platform to add some features. <br /><br /> In addition, the tool was also located in the management of public cloud, within the network and hosting platform to establish the link between.</font>','empty\n'),(339,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/71/2134.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Embrace the open source enterprise software companies say no big deal','Embrace_the_open_source_enterprise_software_companies_say_no_big_deal','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Under the conditions of the economic downturn, big software companies through multi-year licensing agreement with locking customers into a highlight of the strategy. Under the agreement, the software in increasing annual fees, even if the customer corporate downsizing, software licenses will not be reduced. The strategy involves a large software company, leading to &quot;keep shelf software&quot; and re-trap the discount structure, plus an additional charge. Between entities such as software migration charges, the current hardware or via the Internet to access the customer\'s own data, and also an additional charge. <br /><br /> Large software company\'s strategy in the four decades has been a very brilliant art, have so many people have become rich. This strategy is now in a very difficult market environment is still effective. This year there are at least two companies - Oracle and SAP customers of its software for the existing rate of 18% price increase. <br /><br /> But a lot of smart enterprise customers have adopted a new software business models, to avoid the rigid nature of large software companies and financial burden. <br /><br /> James - Sims (James Sims) is a multi-billion dollar annual revenues Save Mart merchandise retailer\'s IT vice president and chief information officer, he is a very large software company\'s strategy bore. Before he started taking Open Source, Save Mart 250 stores, three warehouses and a fleet of 20,000 service staff and IT systems using Oracle, Microsoft and other big software vendors software. Sims said the past few years, Oracle is very arrogant attitude of their company, services is very bad. So he made to the Oracle, Save Mart can solve the Oracle can not solve the problem. Simms has not kept his word. <br /><br /> Sims with SuSe Linux operating system, Ingres open source database deployment, IT infrastructure to open source technology to replace proprietary software, open source monitoring tools for monitoring the use of Hobbit Save Mart server, application software and network &quot;health&quot; status. He also worked with Novell, Red Hat and Ingres alliance to support open source software. <br /><br /> Sims said that open source software and proprietary software is not only easy to use, in many cases, even easier to use than proprietary software. He also said that since open source solutions to replace the Oracle, Microsoft and HP\'s proprietary software, each year for 50% of the IT companies to save costs. <br /><br /> Simms said: &quot;Too many IT organizations prefer to maintain the status quo solution, but time will tell our extremely aggressive and innovative is not wrong. Riyongbaihuo 2% net profit can be quite good, so even if the cut one-tenth the cost of even one percent, its meaning is quite significant. Our IT department operating expenses accounted for 0.37% of revenue, compared with their peers, our IT spending accounted for only half of their average expenditure. and other daily department store retailers, our IT department at a lower price to provide higher quality services. We save every penny will directly reduce customer costs. &quot; <br /><br /> Investment bank Cowen Group Chief Information Officer Daniel - Fourah Kesi (Daniel Flax) in the proprietary software, and cost less stiff, it begins to concern about open source solutions. He is not sacrificing quality, performance, under the premise of low-cost alternative to expensive programs open source solutions. <br /><br /> The goal is threefold: to develop a new method of cost-effectiveness; strengthen the competitive edge to provide maximum returns for shareholders; requirements within each Cowen IT projects include at least mobility, software as a service (SaaS) and open source software, the three elements the two. <br /><br /> Fula Kesi Ingres database performance and expected performance of proprietary databases as well, but cost only one-tenth of proprietary databases. He is an important item to consider a series of programmed trading database, after considering the cost, maturity and functionality of selected Ingres. He is also concerned over MySQL, but worried about Sun MySQL acquisition by Oracle\'s future is uncertain. <br /><br /> Select commercial open source solutions, Cowen Group do not pay renewal fees (transfer of rights from one party to another when the need to pay the costs), multi-core pricing, software license renewals, no additional support costs. Companies to make significant adjustments to the budget, investment and innovative IT projects, to achieve the goal Cowen and Fula Kesi. <br /><br /> Australian oil and margarine company Peerless Foods to independent development of the enterprise resource planning system (ERP), its chief information officer Adrian - Hamilton (Adrian Hamilton) on the management of Peerless products from paper to commercial software distributors are not satisfied. He expressed concern over commercial module software, but in their retreat before the high cost. <br /><br /> As the business continues to grow, Peerless need a more compatible, more flexible platform to adapt to the modern production environment to support future expansion. Most companies have similar backgrounds choose proprietary software vendors, and Peerless has decided to completely build their own ERP and business intelligence solutions.</font>','empty\n'),(340,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/9f/2126.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Linus said: Linux kernel fat, lose weight!','Linus_said_Linux_kernel_fat_lose_weight','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">September 22 Beijing time, according to media reports, on Monday at the <a class=\"kw\" href=\"/article/d4/444.html\">Linux</a> Con Technology Conference, <a class=\"kw\" href=\"/article/d4/444.html\">Linux</a> operating system founder, known as &quot;Linux father,&quot; said Linus Torvalds (Linus Torvalds), said , the current <a class=\"kw\" href=\"/article/d4/444.html\">Linux</a> kernel become bigger and bigger, more complex functions, although this follow-up code to make integration easier, but top priority should be on the Linux kernel, or &quot;thin&quot;, so the kernel can be more concise .</font> <p><font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Ã£Â€Â€Ã£Â€Â€</font></p><p align=\"center\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\"><img alt=\"&quot;Linux&quot; Father Linus Torvalds (Artesyn Technologies with map)\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://digital.ynet.com/imagelist/2009/265/5g9as83re78e.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></font> </p><p align=\"center\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">&quot;Linux&quot; Father Linus Torvalds</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Torvalds said: &quot;The great volume of Linux kernel, this is indeed a problem. I envisioned 15 years ago Linux kernel size should be very simple, and not so bloated as it is now.&quot; He then said that every time the Linux kernel add new features, the bloated size of the problem of the kernel emerged. Linux kernel faster to add new features, a system the higher the chance of vulnerabilities.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Linux Foundation recently released a report that the recent past, Linux kernel development was accelerated rate trend, more outside developers have been gradually added to the ranks of Linux developers.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Torvalds expressed that, with more developers are very pleased to join this case, because the Linux developers faster, his own work easier, &quot;Compared with six months ago, our current development model seems to have more effective. and now developed by other developers to improve the quality stuff, I also more easily get the code to Linux kernel were to go. &quot;</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Motivation to change</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Torvalds also said Linux kernel is currently developing their own motives and have been very different than before. He had started developing Linux kernel, the motivation is very simple: want to know about computer hardware and software, between, and developed their own hands &quot;cool&quot; work. Now, his motivation has become: how to make the Linux community size for further development.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Torvalds said: &quot;I like to argue with others, I like to tell people they are stupid. My first question for the computer technology has long been resolved. I did not do this on a computer to solve the problem myself, I do a very interesting and valuable things. &quot;</font> </p>','empty\n'),(341,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/1d/2125.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Zhang Wen Song LVS joined the founder of Taobao','Zhang_Wen_Song_LVS_joined_the_founder_of_Taobao','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">The afternoon of Sept. 22, according to the relevant person in charge confirmed that Taobao, the international project LVS ( <a class=\"kw\" href=\"/article/d4/444.html\">Linux</a> Virtual Server), founder of Dr. Zhang Wen-Sung will soon join the dragons, and served as head of research and development.</font> <p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">It is reported that Zhang Wen Song will be responsible for leading the R &amp; D core system Taobao, Taobao based primarily responsible for core software development, promote the network hardware and software performance optimization, and build the next generation of low carbon Taobao e-commerce systems based on low-cost platform work.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Zhang Wen-Sung was born in 1973, received his Ph.D. at the National Defense University. In 1998, Zhang Wen-Sung founded LVS and become a major developer, had also served as chief scientist TelTel engaged in large-scale distributed communication system design and development.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">LVS is the <a class=\"kw\" href=\"/article/d4/444.html\">Linux</a> Virtual Server acronym, meaning that <a class=\"kw\" href=\"/article/d4/444.html\">Linux</a> virtual server. LVS cluster using IP load balancing technology and content-based request distribution technology, you can request balance transfer to a different server running, which will be a group of servers to form a high-performance, highly available virtual servers.</font> </p>','It is reported that Zhang Wen Song will be responsible for leading the R & D core system Taobao, Taobao based primarily responsible for core software development, promote the network hardware and software performance optimization, and build the next generation of low carbon Taobao e-commerce systems...'),(342,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/75/2122.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Google China President Kai-fu Lee to leave business','Google_China_President_Kaifu_Lee_to_leave_business','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Google Vice President, Greater China president Kai-fu Lee will officially resign today, in the four-year term after the end of the final choice to leave. According to reliable sources Kai-fu Lee said possible future self-employed. Thus, since 2005, Google officially incorporated into China since the founding team has fully left.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">We failed to contact Google and Kai-fu Lee Chinese officials for comment. But in an exclusive inside information learned in the show, Kai-fu Lee on August 5 this year, leaving the application submitted, and rejected Google\'s invitation to its renewal.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">It is believed that Google China will be officially announced this morning the news, many internal staff informed of this in advance. Despite constant reports of previous years, had been left Kai-fu Lee rumors, but this is indeed the news is still so many people were shocked. Including Google executives, including CEO Eric Schmidt has even behind Kai-fu Lee to visit China.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Kai-fu Lee was hired away from Google and Microsoft battle in one of the most controversial. July 2005 when he was vice president of Microsoft, Kai-fu Lee quit Google, as the president of Google China, Microsoft immediately to non-competition grounds in the United States will Google and Kai-fu Lee to court, the two sides in December that year a secret settlement.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Joining Google four years of Kai-fu Lee has led the China team to develop the market, from the early recruitment, formation of companies to the late development partners, the introduction of localization services, success will Google market share in China from 2006\'s 16.1% rise to the current 31%.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Kai-fu Lee\'s sudden departure, may make the already weak position in the business again, Google China have a strong impact. Its main rival Baidu is currently being further strengthen its leading position in the market, and in term of Kai-fu Lee had just a slight improvement of the localization project: such as the introduction of Google\'s products, such as may be affected.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Google has not specified the current candidates. Kai-fu Lee in 2005 and formed with two other Google executives in China: Chou marketing director in charge of the market, respectively, Wang Huainan have long been resigned. According to speculation, the current head of Google Greater China sales may be global to succeed John Liu, vice president Kai-fu Lee.</font> </p>','Google Vice President, Greater China president Kai-fu Lee will officially resign today, in the four-year term after the end of the final choice to leave. According to reliable sources Kai-fu Lee said possible future self-employed. Thus, since 2005, Google officially incorporated into China since the...'),(343,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/e5/2116.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Oracle has surpassed Microsoft to become the number one killer of open source?','Oracle_has_surpassed_Microsoft_to_become_the_number_one_killer_of_open_source','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p> <span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"http://www.ixpub.net/tag.php?name=%CE%A2%C8%ED\" onclick=\"tagshow(event)\">Microsoft</span> had previously been regarded as the number one killer of open source, operating <span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"http://www.ixpub.net/tag.php?name=%CF%B5%CD%B3\" onclick=\"tagshow(event)\">system,</span> <span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"http://www.ixpub.net/tag.php?name=%CA%FD%BE%DD%BF%E2\" onclick=\"tagshow(event)\">database,</span> office <span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"http://www.ixpub.net/tag.php?name=%C8%ED%BC%FE\" onclick=\"tagshow(event)\">software,</span> security, software, <span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"http://www.ixpub.net/tag.php?name=%BF%AA%B7%A2\" onclick=\"tagshow(event)\">development</span> <span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"http://www.ixpub.net/tag.php?name=%B9%A4%BE%DF\" onclick=\"tagshow(event)\">tools,</span> browser ... ... Microsoft, both online and in almost every open source products have a fierce contest. But playing for so many years, we found that not only rivals Microsoft\'s open source does not fall, but all of them have expanded the site, access to the <span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"http://www.ixpub.net/tag.php?name=%D3%C3%BB%A7\" onclick=\"tagshow(event)\">user</span> favor. Microsoft\'s combat effectiveness is not it? Or shot is not cruel? <br /><br /> In my opinion, Microsoft is also considered best. <br /><br /> Earlier to move about SUN\'s JAVA, unexpect