talented people, the National Main talented, but can not stop Rulangsihu the Zhao brothers. After the annexation of the State, so beloved by others ruined. <br /></p><p> <strong><font color=\"#ecf4f5\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net\">www.ixdba.net</a></font></strong> </p><br /><br /> Anyway, I still would like to thank McNealy here. In his &quot;offer the city&quot; before the moment has its own fully open source product. Although the independent company is gone, but the flames of revolution, but with tolerance and generosity Sun then spread to various open source organizations, companies. MariaDB such as MySQL branch has to grow up. <br /> It is believed that, Sun\'s other open source products, will have their proper successor to carry forward. And Oracle, open source projects that the number of endangered executioner, if they are not Fanran repentance, after all, one day camp was open violent retaliation.','Microsoft had previously been regarded as the number one killer of open source, operating system, database, office software, security, software, development tools, browser ... ... Microsoft, both online and in almost every open source products have a fierce contest. But playing for so many years, we...'),(344,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/cc/2096.html','http://www.ixdba.net','2009 grand opening of the system architect Tai Hui! Topic: system architecture, networking, storage, servers, databases','2009_grand_opening_of_the_system_architect_Tai_Hui_Topic_system_architecture_networking_storage_servers_databases','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">8.28 Beijing: 2009 system architect Tai Hui grand opening! ! Topic locking: system architecture, networking, storage, servers, databases</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">System architects, according to the understanding of most enterprises, it is not an administrative job, but a title. Nevertheless, it is a large number of application developers, operations managers career development goals. In many cases, the system architect is to ensure the sustainability of the backbone of business-critical applications, is to construct the creator of enterprise system architecture.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">In this context, we IT168 (ChinaUnix, ITPUB, IXPUB) hosted the 2009 system architect Assembly, to provide face to face for the system architects of high-level technical exchange platform. System architecture with everyone and discuss various issues. For example: <br /> How to design a system architecture to address future enterprise-scale development (the development of business-critical traffic)? <br /> How to design the application server resources to achieve performance and cost savings point of balance? <br /> How to plan network infrastructure, effective management of business-critical load, to prevent access to bottleneck traffic? <br /> How to manage the increasing scale of storage of data, how to manage concurrent access to data backup?</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Need of special note: we IT168 (ChinaUnix, ITPUB, IXPUB) had organized a series of General Assembly of free technical salon, but this time the cost of AA Technical Conference will implement the system, the need for participants to implement the charging system. Therefore we do not want to profit, mainly: This is a systems architect open event for everyone in the same time, it should be paying the price for their share.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">The Technology Conference, we invited a large lineup of experts, all on-site analysis of successful cases for the practice, with a high practical value, such as: <br /> 1, a large scalable system architecture application platform for dynamic practice Sina Tong Jian: Sina, Director of Platform R &amp; D Center</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">2, the electronic payment systems and open distributed service architecture framework of Cheng Li: Alipay (China) Chief Architect</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">3, Mysql databases online disaster recovery practice analysis Xu Jingchun: 51.com database competent</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">4, Mysql pressure limit test reporting practices Shaozong Wen: Sina senior database specialist, director of database platform</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">5, highly available distributed database system architecture practice Ji-Ping Chen: Taobao Principal DBA, DBA Manager</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">6, distributed file system to store data management bottlenecks MFS crack, senior systems architect Tin Yat</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">7, case practice, how to determine the structure of the whole system monitoring framework Cao Shijun: Beijing Fukatsu Century System Architect</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">8, explore the architecture of the sixth sense (Sina) <br /> Li Xiaodong: Sina Technical Manager R &amp; D structure <br /> ......</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">More speech topics, speech person, please click: <br /> System Architect 2009 Conference - official website (Technology Conference details) <br /> <a href=\"http://net.it168.com/focus/200906/sacc2009/index.html\">http://net.it168.com/focus/200906/sacc2009/index.html</a></font> <br /> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">System Architect Registration 2009 Conference, please click: <br /> <a href=\"http://net.it168.com/focus/200906/sacc2009/include/4.html\">http://net.it168.com/focus/200906/sacc2009/include/4.html</a></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Tai Hui Title: System Architect Group Conference 2009 Location: Gehua New Century Hotel. Beijing Conference Time: 2009.8.28 ~ 8.29 (two days) <br /> Structure of the agenda: <br /> Time Speaker Topic (first day) <br /> Scale <br /> 8.28 am Technical Conference home: the overall design of the system architecture 500-600 people <br /> 8.28 pm Technical Session 1: Network Architecture Design Session 200-300 <br /> 8.28 pm Technical Session 2: Application Server Architecture Design Session 200-300 <br /> 8.28 topic at dinner (dinner points table, the free exchange of time) <br /> 100-150</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">The next day <br /><br /> 8.29 am Technical Session 3: Open the database architecture design special 200-300 <br /> 8.29 am Technical Forum 4: System Monitoring, Security Session 200-300 <br /> 8.29 pm Technical Forum 5: Session storage architecture design optimization 200-300 <br /> 8.29 pm Session Sharon education sector: enterprise architecture design combined with practical education industry <br /> <strong><font color=\"#ecf4f5\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"><a href=\"http://bbs.ixdba.net\">IXDBA.NET Community Forums</a></font></strong> <br /> 200-300</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">All inquiries, please contact us, please see the conference website. <br /> TANG Chuan 6.28 <br /> IT168 (ChinaUnix, ITPUB, IXPUB) <br /></font> </p>','8.28 Beijing: 2009 system architect Tai Hui grand opening! ! Topic locking: system architecture, networking, storage, servers,...'),(345,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/95/2084.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Yahoo statistical operations off the assembly line, the data shift quantum statistics Hang Road','Yahoo_statistical_operations_off_the_assembly_line_the_data_shift_quantum_statistics_Hang_Road','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<div align=\"center\"><div class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" id=\"attachment_316\" style=\"WIDTH: 314px\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\"><img alt=\"Ã©Â›Â…Ã¨Â™ÂŽÃ§Â»ÂŸÃ¨Â®Â¡Ã¤Â¸ÂŽÃ©Â‡ÂÃ¥Â­ÂÃ¦ÂÂ’Ã©ÂÂ“LOGO\" class=\"size-full wp-image-316\" height=\"176\" src=\"/hbcms/upload/image/big/06/06e507d50a3ffb86c90924f6b5f84c1f.gif\" title=\"Yahoo Hang Road, LOGO and Quantum Statistics\" width=\"304\" /></font> <p class=\"wp-caption-text\"> <font face=\"Tahoma\" size=\"2\">Yahoo Hang Road, LOG