w.ixdba.net','Look down from the SUN recession duel between technology and business capital','Look_down_from_the_SUN_recession_duel_between_technology_and_business_capital','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Acquisition of information of a sudden woke IT IT world, all different, surprising at the same time, allows us to see this long-hidden behind a large M &amp; A stories and thought-provoking topic.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">In 2000, Sun server is the darling of Wall Street financial users; 2009, Sun became a profitable long-lost shareholders outcast, a piece of paper 7.4 billion contract, Sun\'s Board of Directors and Oracle had a good talk.</font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Although market revenue is not high, but Sun is still a large degree of influence it vane technology, contributed most to the source code for open source companies in the broadest sense not to wait until the advent of open source market, which will have an open, free good people are sad. Oracle announced the acquisition of Sun With the news came, &quot;Sun said the acquisition&quot; of the initiator can finally be justified in their time, but to see a larger, its technology may prevent the development of strategies to competitors, this is clearly a irony. <br /></font> </p><p> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">It can be said McNealy, Sun\'s soul, often face the outside of his casual style in the pursuit of technology strategy is to have a &quot;paranoid&quot; heart. To know that Sun is the industry\'s R &amp; D / sales ratio of top manufacturers, even in recent years, Sun\'s R &amp; D investment has remained at 15 to 20 billion dollars in revenue a year to know the Sun only in his early 10 billion U.S. dollars (the Oracle\'s acquisition of a total of 7.4 billion, while the removal of Sun\'s cash and debt, excluding the net value of transactions of 56 billion U.S. dollars, only about three years, Sun, R &amp; D investment. and IBM out of the price tag would go low $ 900,000,000 .) <br /><br /> The high R &amp; D investment and market performance is almost two separate issues, Sun is the most glorious era in September 2000, when the Sun stock price close to 260 dollars. But the most advanced information technology company in a very long time and do not realize that &quot;wine is also afraid of themselves&quot;, but at this time, the elephant learned to dance, HP will be a substantial expansion of the business, the companies have annual turnover of billions of dollars into the threshold. Sun is billions of dollars to market the club further away, and this standard is considered to restore the confidence of a large fund companies the baseline, falling stock prices for these large funds are losing confidence. The result of selling shares they are so gradual Sun shares fell $ 5, $ 4, $ 3 ... ... <br /><br /> Beginning in 2007, Sun will promote the gradual shift from a hardware software, solutions, and then clear the &quot;integration of network and computing&quot; as the Sun\'s core idea of &quot;open source&quot; as the Sun\'s market-oriented. 10 billion acquisition of mysql after, Sun still insists on open-source operating mode, and core technology open source solaris and sparc processor Sun is sufficient proof of courage. Sun believe that the future of the world is an open, free, &quot;the network is the computer&quot; has become a reality from the slogan, but Sun did not wait until the &quot;open source&quot; market penetration of that day. <br /><br /> Sun\'s stock price kept falling, we can say &quot;The acquisition of&quot; the advocates of credit. &quot;Only by the acquisition, Sun has been in dire straits can be saved.&quot; Spread of such statements in the shaken confidence of users to buy the same time, Sun is also shaking the morale of the troops, while allowing them a leader in Empire of the Sun exhausted. Sun Tech Days 2008 held in Beijing, the face with a tired color McNealy in a speech after which they face from the media, &quot;the acquisition of&quot; challenges. After about one and a half months, Sun shares fell into a historical low - $ 2.83. Even so, capital market is still not seize the opportunity to acquisitions, and perhaps they think it is still not reached the bottom of the market value of Sun, and perhaps they still want Sun to the hands of the 30 billion dollars in cash is running out. When the Sun 2009q2 better than expected earnings news, when Sun began to &quot;optimize it&quot; Moving services market, capital market began to realize that they have missed the opportunity to start low. Ever since, Washington Post broke the news &quot;For the acquisition of Blue Sun.&quot; However, because IBM is suspected of committing monopoly, and Sun want to offer more, and especially from within Sun\'s McNealy who were stranded strong opposition. This event took place in two weeks, Sun has gone from $ 4.70 share price rose $ 8.89, and the curve fell to $ 6.28.</font> </p><p><br /> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Financial magazine &quot;Forbes&quot; announced: &quot;Following the company was willing to IBM after the acquisition will not, Sun will regret not to accept the original price.&quot; Like the Sun\'s share price did not fall to the level before, and even increased by 33%, which Sun describes the market for at least the company still has a very strong faith, but also on the &quot;buy&quot; argument gives the holder of a direct reply: &quot;If the Sun did not value, IBM Why fancy it?&quot;</font> </p>','Acquisition of information of a sudden woke IT IT world, all different, surprising at the same time, allows us to see this long-hidden behind a large M & A stories and thought-provoking...'),(347,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/80/2067.html','http://www.ixdba.net','On the oracle and insider view of the acquisition of SUN','On_the_oracle_and_insider_view_of_the_acquisition_of_SUN','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p> <fo