er hardware as a means of promotion, so that rival those of hardware servers is no small blow. <br /><br /> 6, Sun has sold 1.6 to 2 million servers, and many more operating systems running Sun Solaris servers of other companies. This is Oracle\'s bundling of its products is also helpful. <br /><br /> 7, Oracle\'s acquisition of Sun, of course, including open-source database MySQL. Modest budget, but for those who need to users of Oracle products, Oracle can use MySQL to meet the needs of these users. This allows Oracle to enter small and medium business, more opportunities in this regard than SAP. In addition, it also provides competitive products and Microsoft SQLServer, without the need to reduce the positioning of Oracle\'s own products. <br /><br /> Oracle and Sun co-operation may affect Oracle\'s relationship with some partners, such as Oracle and HP\'s relationship may be a problem. However, unlike IBM, in fact, each of the hardware companies are not open around the Oracle database because it is the main force. Oracle can not do without them, so they can only chose to keep silent. <br /> Moreover, with the Sun and IBM jointly different, Oracle and Sun hardware conflict does not exist, those who do not have to worry about Sun\'s server customers to abandon their merger will lead to the use of the server product line. <br /><br /> All in all, a relatively low price Oracle, Sun acquired is wise, after the merger will make Oracle a major hub for corporate data centers.</font> <div style=\"DISPLAY: none\"></div></p>','Beijing April 20, Oracle and Sun Microsystems issued a joint statement, Oracle 7.4 billion acquisition of Sun. Analysis of articles published in foreign media, said Oracle\'s acquisition of the wisdom of Sun at 7 large:  1, if cloud computing becomes more important for enterprises, then the data...'),(348,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/5a/2048.html','http://www.ixdba.net','My analysis: sun When will drained?','My_analysis_sun_When_will_drained','2010-1