fiber optic line, where the host need to execute cfgmgr, in fact, send a signal to the optical switch, otherwise, optical switching not recognize the card WWN, This does not cost any time before. I configured through Step 4, Step 5, I checked dell\'s engineers, there is indeed a connection state route 4, all normal, then begin to step 6.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">We first removed by rmdev-dl recognized previous to the disk array, to identify with the cfgmgr-v and found that only two paths, and even under theÃ§Â‹Â Ã¦Â‹Â›, rmdev-Rdl fcs (x), delete the entire fiber cards , the re-recognition, or only two paths. We began depressed, so the engineers began to call dell, we began to check.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Optical fiber switch certainly normal, you can see all of the optical card.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Ã‚Â· Zone configuration certainly nothing wrong configuration enable the</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">* Path certainly normal, cx700, you can see four channels are normal</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">dell\'s engineers call the same time, IBM\'s engineers do not forget to ask, &quot;where we are normal, should be your problem&quot;</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">IBM engineer said, &quot;disk are not recognized, the question should be, where you have&quot;</font> </p><p><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Time so passed, and I think it is a problem where, in fact, that is, suddenly, thought would not be cx700\'s store group, where there is a problem normally, store group which only determines which hosts can access lun, should not be a problem, but now linked with the host, and only him. Immediate action, I first host to delete all the disk array, and then I HA from the store group in the host kicked out, to be sure. Came alive again in, confirmation, re-recognition on the host disk, normal.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">dell\'s engineers on the phone then, and I cried with ibm engineers then, &quot;Brother, do not call as it has been good.&quot;</font> </p><p> <strong><font color=\"#ecf4f5\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net\">www.ixdba.net</a></font></strong> </p><br /><p><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">This problem is well, discovered a new problem, because we removed too fast, did not recognize the hard disk out of the information PVID and VG, while the HA this is the machine, these drives are actually being used, can not be used the conventional method to obtain PVID and VG information, that is, we can not use normal importvg to import VG, there is no way to use the chdev-l hdiskpower (x)-a pv = yes PVID and VG way to get information. <br /> How to do? This is just great, dell engineer with ibm go go for help.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">What results did not seek help, then I can only come ruthless, because the machine can not perform importvg HA reason is because the master node also using the VG, then the temporary lifting of the lock is not on it.</font> </p><pre style=\"BACKGROUND: #e6e6e6; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Master node: varyonvg-b-u vgname # # # HA unlock the machine: importvg-L vgname hdiskpower (x) # # # read the information master: varyonvg vgname # # # lock</font> </pre><p><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Note that the above operation has risks, especially in concurrent systems, such as could not be unlocked on the RAC, is the single node, the unlock operation should be cautious. Because we here in the evening, the pressure is small, but time is short, relationship is not big.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">After the above operation, HA finally normal. Then think about the whole story, in fact, we have ignored the store group is there, I guess store group to go in the path information to the record (or is cached up), because it is the final decision on what the host can use any LUN, But he should not decided the number of paths. The second problem arises, it is because we are anxious to solve the first problem, using some unconventional operations on the scene.</font> </p>','empty\n'),(385,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/b8/1038.html','http://www.ixdba.net','orion - a good memory test IO','orion__a_good_memory_test_IO','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">orion, a company by the Oracle provided the database used to simulate the operating mechanism specifically to test the memory of outstanding IO memory test software, you can not run the case of oracle database, OLTP simulation of random operation (test IOPS) or continuous operation OLAP (test throughput.)</font> <p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Look at the software download address and description:</font> </p><pre style=\"BACKGROUND: #e6e6e6; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">ORION is the Oracle I / O Numbers Calibration Tool designed to\r\n    simulate Oracle I / O workloads\r\n    - Without having to create and run an Oracle database\r\n    - Using the Oracle database\'s I / O libraries\r\n    - Using small I / Os to simulate OLTP workloads\r\n    - Using large I / Os to simulate data warehouses\r\n\r\n    ORION is useful for understanding the performance capabilities of a storage system,\r\n    either to uncover performance issues or to size a new database installation.\r\n    The Users Guide contains a Getting Started section, detailed usage documentation,\r\n    and trouble-shooting tips. Please note that ORION is not supported by Oracle. \r\n\r\n    Download the files:\r\n     Ã‚Â· Orion_AIX64.gz (11,670,726 bytes)\r\n     Ã‚Â· Orion_solaris64_sparc.gz (898,929 bytes)\r\n     Ã‚Â· Orion_solaris_x8664.gz (655,975 bytes)\r\n     Ã‚Â· Orion_linux_em64t.gz (767,380 bytes)\r\n     Ã‚Â· Orion10.2_linux.gz (630,354 bytes)\r\n     Ã‚Â· Orion10.2_windows.msi (7,865,856 bytes)\r\n     Ã‚Â· Users Guide\r\n</font> </pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Can see, this software has support for multiple OS environments, unfortunately, Oracle does not provide services to support the software, but this does not affect the normal use of the software, test results from my point of view, the software really is a very good memory testing software.</font> </p><p><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Downloaded to the software, have separately compiled without any compiler that can run their own OS environment, the stress test than many other software needs to recompile a lot better, but also more convenient, for example, in the AIX environment, in extracted directory, run. / orion-help, which you can see the details of the software help.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">The software supports three operation modes</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Simple: simple test of small random IO (the default 8k) and large IO (the default 1024K), this approach to initial run the software, or general understanding of the basic characteristics of useful storage.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Normal: IO of different types can be combined, but still can not customize the size of IO</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Advanced: to support a variety of advanced options, such as the IO size, pressure, size, IO types, testing methods, etc.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Two different ways, and the pressure</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">A typical OLTP environment: Choose a small random IO, test storage can support the maximum IOPS and response time</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Typical OLAP environment: the selection order of the large IO, storage can support the maximum test throughput and response time</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">The software to run only one configuration file, &lt;testname&gt;. Lun, configure a test of the need to use the disk information, and return the following information:</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">&lt;testname&gt; _iops.csv: IOPS value of different types of pressure</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">&lt;testname&gt; _mbps.csv: the throughput of the different types of pressure</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">&lt;testname&gt; _lat.csv: the response under different types of time pressure</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">&lt;testname&gt; _summary.txt: summary information of test results</font> </p><p><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">I were to run load runner oracle simulation database activities, and just run the software simulation of database activity, it is obvious that the advantages of the software:</font> </p> <strong><font color=\"#ecf4f5\" face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"><a href=\"http://bbs.ixdba.net\">IXDBA.NET Community Forums</a></font></strong> <br /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">1, no need to run load runner, and configure a large number of clinet</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">2, do not need to run the oracle database, and to prepare a large number of test data</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">3, the test results more representative, such as random IO test, the software is able to store the hit rate close to 0, but more realistic simulation of the disk out of the IOPS, while load runner difficult to achieve this, the final disk IOPS need to be converted.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">4, can be customized write a certain percentage (the default does not write), but note that if there is data on the disk, the data need to be careful to be overwritten.</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Of course, also has its drawbacks</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">1, up to now, can not specify a custom run time and the overall magnitude of pressure, here is completely automatic</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">2, can not be some custom action type, such as a table scan operation, load testing, etc., but can be combined with the oracle database to achieve this effect</font> </p><p><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\"></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">Below, I give some specific examples of its operation</font> </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> <font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\">1, the database OLTP type, assuming that all types of 8K random IO operation, pressure type, automatic compression, from small to large, up to storage pressure limit</font> </p>','empty\n'),(386,'BLOG','BLOG','en','/article/94/1039.html','http://www.ixdba.net','Multiplexing fiber-optic network - DWDM','Multiplexing_fiberoptic_network__DWDM','2010-11-12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Next, we look at a simple typical SAN environment, we have 2 hosts, 2 SAN switches, 2 storage, they may be HA, it may be RAC environment, perhaps the single, this is not important. Importantly, the SAN environment, we are generally configured in the local, similar to a local area network, we use fiber-optic cable generally can build such a SAN environment. <p></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img alt=\"dwdm\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/dwdm1.jpg\" title=\"dwdm\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> Now, because of business needs, you must consider disaster recovery, you want these two machines, 2 sets of storage located in a different room, which more than two rooms separated by a 10KM, if forcibly opened, we will see is this some kind. </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img alt=\"dwdm\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/dwdm2.jpg\" title=\"dwdm\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> You can see, there are a lot of fiber need to be pulled very long, so long fiber, do not rely on operators, is generally no way to pull their own. Moreover, the more fiber, will bring the greater the cost. So, we do not have a good solution to it? Or some, this is the DWDM (DenseWavelength-Division Multiplexing, high-density multi-work-point filter) optical multiplexing, according to the development of over DWDM WDM technology has been widely used for many years, and after the use of DWDM will become the SAN structure look. </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img alt=\"dwdm\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/dwdm3.jpg\" title=\"dwdm\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> As a result of optical multiplexing, so the long-distance fiber-optic cable now only need one, that is considered redundant, but also as long as the two on it. The use of such methods, the whole structure has not changed, you can run that line in that fiber is the fiber you need more than root. </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> DWDM is how it possible? We look at a schematic </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img alt=\"dwdm\" src=\"http://www.ixdba.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/dwdm4.jpg\" title=\"dwdm\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> Simply put, DWDM optical fiber line is actually a different wavelength to pass different data to simulate different channel, the actual looks like a different fiber in communications, not the same wavelength as long as you can, so DWDM a fiber optic line can be easily reused dozens of channels (channels), lab or even a few thousand multiplexed channels. </p><p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"> So, with this thing, access to remote storage through the SAN to become very easy, RAC is no longer a remote dream. In fact, through this DWDM technology and then copy the volume to disaster recovery technology in a domestic banking institutions has been officially in use. Moreover, the remote RAC, a new disaster recovery plan that can achieve high availability and load balancing, and disaster recovery programs can also use the company to consider. </p>','empty\n');
